(69, '67', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Italy;Somalia', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mum was born in Somalia she moved to Italy because of a war. A few years later (2005) my mum was pregnant with me then she moved to London.', 'Family;Italy;Somalia;Third person;War', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
