(93, '90', NULL, NULL, '1940s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Forced Migration/Enslavement', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, 'Germany', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandfather Horst Hoffmann arrived in the UK as a POW in 1945 and decided to claim refugee status rather than go back to Berlin, Germany. He raised a family in Nottingham but never lost his accent.', 'Assimilation;Culture;Family;Germany;Language;Third person;War', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1),
