(795, '793', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ireland;india', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'John Keatinge 1850s left Ireland, jointed the 9-Foot and went to India. He was my 2xgreat\ngrandfather. He stayed in India in the Army. My mother was born in India and came to England in the 1920’s.', 'Third Person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
