(827, '825', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Departures', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'I know I’m a King, chip on my shoulder, I was sinking, didn’t know that I could leave, blood in the water, I was walking in my sleep.', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
