(1370, '1368', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I emigrated here as a student then went back to my country. A few years after I migrated again. If anyone asks about who I am: I’d say: I am a migrant!', 'Education;Pride', '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', NULL, 0, 0),
(1371, '1369', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'Lots of different migration stories. Wars and why people would be a refugee, migrant, emigrant, and immigrant.', 'War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', NULL, 0, 0),
(1372, '1370', NULL, NULL, '1980s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Somalia', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents and their family immigrated from Somalia due to the start of civil war.', 'Family;Somalia;War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', NULL, 0, 0),
(1373, '1371', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Poland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mum migrated here from Poland.', 'Family;Poland', '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', NULL, 0, 0),
(1374, '1372', 'Eleanor', NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'Both my parents and all of my grandparents were born in Britain. But we think migration is important. Eleanor aged 4.', 'Family', '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', 'aged 4', 0, 0),
(1375, '1373', NULL, NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandma was born in 1936 and in 1956 she migrated to England and worked in a factory and then after she worked in a factory, she worked in a hospital', 'Family;Healthcare;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', NULL, 0, 0),
(1376, '1374', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'I would like to see a drawing table. ', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', NULL, 0, 0),
(1377, '1375', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'Dynamic culture with sounds, food, specific goods that can represent mixed culture. Like fork and chopsticks in one family ', 'Culture;Food;Music', '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', NULL, 0, 0),
(1378, '1376', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Brazil', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'I have a mixed family made by the war. I am French, English, Spanish and Portuguese but I was born in Brazil.', 'Brazil;Ethnicity;Family;France;Spain;Portugal;War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', 'Correct disc?', 0, 0),
(1379, '1377', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, '(AS FAR AS I KNOW) I found these stories very moving. I am proud of Britain. We are welcoming – and we are FREE – aren’t we lucky.', 'Culture;Pride', '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', NULL, 0, 0),
(1380, '1378', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Brunei;Cyprus;Germany;Nigeria', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandparents live in Germany > Brunei> Cyprus> Nigeria where my mum was born > back to Cyprus and then settled in the UK. ', 'Brunei;Cyprus;Family;Germany;Nigeria;Third Person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', NULL, 0, 0),
(1381, '1379', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents migrated here for me and my brother to have a better upbringing environment. Now I want to emigrate away for better opportunities.', 'Family', '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', NULL, 0, 0),
(1382, '1380', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'China', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My great Aunt migrated here and raised a family. My grandma migrated to America to raise me when my parents couldn’t. in doing so she sacrificed more than I could ever thank her for, when she came here with nothing, she sacrificed her freedom and happiness to ensure the next generation will grow up well. My parents didn’t graduate high school because they were required by the government to move to the villages to farm and train to be soldiers. They lived in straw houses, scarcely ate, awoke at 3 am to march miles to train at 5am with heavy packs on their backs. They came back to their families aged 23 and worked constructing houses. They moved to America California in hopes that they would be able to give me greater access to education, so I wouldn’t have to suffer like they did. But the situation in America is dire so perhaps I too will have to migrate to give my children the same opportunities. China to America ', 'China;Education;Family;Politics;Pride;Third Person;USA;Wellbeing;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', 'Great-aunt migrated to UK', 0, 0),
(1383, '1381', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'Something to do with comfort food, and what a taste of honey means to you?  A national dish, street food, a family recipe, a particular custom?', 'Food', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1384, '1382', NULL, NULL, '1990s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came here in 1996 as a post-student working holiday maker.  Now I’m settled with 4 children and working on immigration.', 'education;family', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1385, '1383', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, '100% Anglo-Saxon – but could consider myself a European.  My partner is from South Pacific, and my nieces and nephews from Turkey, West Indies, France and Uganda (to varying degrees).  Love London', 'family', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1386, '1384', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, '1931	Shoreditch 1933	Napoli 1916 Holland 1966 Chelyablingk 1967 Christian 1966 Jewish', 'Family;third person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1387, '1385', NULL, NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My great granma came to the UK from Jamaica in 1952.  She was a nurse\n', 'thrid person;work', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1388, '1386', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Je suis a Londres dans le but d’appredre la langue, mais sur-tout, pour vivre une experience unique! Londres es tune ville tres riche en histories et en cultures.', 'education;language', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1389, '1387', NULL, NULL, '1960s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Barbados', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My dad immigrated to England from beautiful Barbados aged 21 in 1960.  He said although he had a nice life and a good job he wanted to see ‘the Motherland’. He stayed in England for 32 years before he finally visited home.', 'culture;third person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1390, '1388', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'China;Malaysia', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mother came from Penang, Malaysia, but her family before that came from China.', 'culture;third person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1391, '1389', NULL, NULL, '1980s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Mum – Ireland to London 1980s', 'thrid person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1392, '1390', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Poland', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to England for the adventure as a young boy of 19.  Travelled from Poland on the bus, still here 15 years on.', 'culture', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1393, '1391', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Africa', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, ' My both sets of grandparents migrated from Africa', 'family;third person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1394, '1392', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Malta;Malaysia', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'Both my parents migrated here separately, my Dad’s family after the war from Malta and m Mum from Malaysia (after she met my dad).', 'family;third person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1395, '1393', NULL, NULL, '1960s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents migrated to the UK in the 60s.  At the time it was difficult to get housing, so they saved by doing a Pardner.  It is like a money club, that’s how many people saved to buy their homes and still do today (2019).', 'community;family;third person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1396, '1394', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Spain', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here in 2005 from Spain. I love the UK: this truly is ‘home’ now.  I have always felt welcome ….. until now.  Brexit has changed everything: the sheer sole of (mainly) English xenophobia and fascism has shocked me deeply.  Now I feel I ought to leave this country.  I no longer feel welcome.', 'alienation;culture;ethnicity;politics', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1397, '1395', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'US', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I’m a student from California.  I attend uni at UC, Davis.  I’m studying at Accent London Study Center through my Uni.  I’ll only be here 18 weeks but I would love to return someday.', 'Culture;Education', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1398, '1396', NULL, NULL, '1980s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Afghanistan Russia', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Born in Afghanistan, in 1984 my mother sent me to Russia for a better future.  As I was not welcomed in Russia, I tried my luck in London.  I arrived here in 1998, learned English, went to uni. What I studied Law and Masters in Law. Now I work as a legal advisor helping other migrants.', 'Assimulation;culture;education;work', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1399, '1397', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Bulgaria', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Ipek S. My from Bulgaria – I am a Turkish girl but my mother is here and I am here to study but I am still here (construction) and like it and I want to stay.', 'education;family', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1400, '1398', 'Ashwa', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Sri lanka ', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My story is that I was born in Sri Lanka and I moved when I was two.  I learned English and Maths so I can communicate with everyone even my friend.', 'community;education;friends', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1401, '1399', NULL, NULL, '1990s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Sweden', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came from Sweden n1997, age 19, to experience London.  I was very lucky to be privileged enough to benefit from free movement and to start a new life in the UK.  Thank you.', 'culture', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1402, '1400', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Bosnia', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I am refugee from Bosnia, where left in Ma 1992, got married to British woman and have 2 kids born here.  Edin Bani', 'asimulation;family', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'taken for HMD', 0, 0),
(1403, '1401', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'South Africa', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I moved to the UK from South Africa when I was 4, my parents wanted a safer way of life.  All  my extended family are still there.', 'family;wellbeing', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1404, '1402', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Germany Russia', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I moved from Russia to Germany in 1991, did an Erasmus year in the UK, fell in love with the country and moved here in 2003.  I have been here longer than anywhere else.  This used to feel like home.  Not anymore.  What now?', 'Alienation;assimilation;culture', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1),
(1405, '1403', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Lithuania', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I moved here to study, then moved to Turkey and after 5 years moved back because I love this country.  Originally from Lithuania.', 'Culture;Education', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1406, '1404', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Mexico', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I moved here 4 years ago to study mathematics from Mexico.  Grateful for the opportunities here!', 'Education', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1407, '1405', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'From Dublin via job opportunities 48 years ago.  I am very happy living in East Sussex.', 'assimulation;work', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1408, '1406', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Morocco', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to be with my father in 2017 from Morocco.  I live in Harrow and I love here and I love his people.  I hope to be (flares?) because I love flowers.  – has stick figures', 'family;work', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1409, '1407', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Australia', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born in Sydney Australia like my brother and stayed there for 2 years because my parents wer working there.  Because of my family in England I moved here.\n', 'family;work', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1410, '1408', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I am ballet dancer, I come to UK because I want to have a bright future.  I can’t have it in my country.', 'wellbeing;work', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1411, '1409', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to England for a better life with my family.  My father is a diplomat and staying here has been a different experience for us.  I am hoping to see more and greater friendships.  Middle Eastern diplomats.\n', 'family;wellbeing', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1412, '1410', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to the UK, my partner did.  My gran-mum’s mum was Slovakian Romanian and my granddad – my dad’s – was Slovak.  I have Czech passport.', 'culture', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1413, '1411', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here because I really wanted to learn English.', 'Education', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1414, '1412', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Today it’s exactly two years I moved to London.  I came here as a street performer and now I am living out of music in London and studying an MA at Goldsmiths.', 'education;music', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1415, '1413', NULL, NULL, '1980s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Finland ', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came from Finland in 1984. Because at that time Finland was not yet part of the EU, I had to carry a small green ‘Aliens Registration Document’.  A lot has changed.  Now they use Euros in Finland but ‘we’ are heading for Brexit.  I have indefinite leave to remain here, but one of my kids, who was born out of the country might face problems even though she has lived here all her life.', 'Family;policies', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1416, '1414', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was three when I moved to England but the reason that I moved to England was because a giant fleet of terrorists came and tried to kill all children in my home country.', 'Genocide;War', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1417, '1415', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came here to stay and have pride in myself.  I was migrated here.  I have love to stay here.  I was migrated here.', 'Pride ', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1418, '1416', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'One my friend came to London to study his master degree.  While he was studying, he knew through his friends that he has to go back because of his family issue.  But he decided to stay more ….', 'Education;Third person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Being Human', 0, 0),
(1419, '1417', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Ireland;Ecuador', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My grandparents migrated to Birmingham from county Lucan, Dublin Ireland. They had my dad and my uncle.  My dad then travelled to South America and met my mother.  Then I cam along born in Quito Ecuador.  We then migrated back to England.  I hope to one day have my own migration story – with the freedom to move anywhere.  How it should be for everyone!', 'Ireland;Ecuador;Family;Third person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1420, '1418', NULL, NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'France', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here from France in 2011, mainly to improve my English.  What was a year top study, ended up in 7.  I’m mixed French, Spanish and Caribbean. I fill in the census form back in 2011 so I’m happily surprise that it’s part of the exhibition.', 'Education;Language;France;Ethnicity', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1421, '1419', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Chile', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'From Chile!  I have been very lucky and felt welcome in the UK since day1.  I can’t even imagine the pain some people endure to get here.  More Love! Less hate.', 'Pride;Assimilation;Chile', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1422, '1420', NULL, 'Snap: Muratganidagli; Insta: Official murat', NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was 9 years od(old) when I moved to the UK with my family.  I’m 23 years old now.  Though this is my home now, I still don’t feel like I am welcomed.', 'Family;Alienation', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1423, '1421', 'Maria', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', 'Economic', NULL, 'Spain', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came here from Spain and one day my dad says we are going to London because  is no job, and my name is Maria and I speak 3 languages Romanian, Spanish and Engles.', 'Family;Work;Spain;Language', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Prendergast Ladywell', 0, 0),
(1424, '1422', 'Har Ying Chan', NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'China', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I am a Chinese girl.  My name is Har Ying Chan.  I am 2012 come to the London.  Stay with my parents.  I was so nervous to been here. (writing in Chinese characters)', 'Family;Wellbeing;China', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1425, '1423', NULL, NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Romania', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My parents migrated to London, and so I moved from Romania to London.  I came in London in 2016 of May.  I move to be to better and to can be with my family.', 'Family;Romania', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Prendergast Ladywell', 0, 0),
(1426, '1424', 'Livia Begum', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Bangladesh', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My name is Livia Begum.  I’m Bengali.  I’m happy to love (live) in this country.', 'Bangladesh', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1427, '1425', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Indonesia', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Born and grew up in Indonesia.  I moved here for Uni he I turned 18.  My family has a long history of moving, with my grandma being born in China to parents who were born in the Philippines and I bet a longer story exists there.  I like being a migrant, but then again, my moving story is a privileged one.  Home is where you hang your hat.   ', 'Pride;Assimilation;Indonesia;Third person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1428, '1426', NULL, NULL, '1990s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', NULL, NULL, 'USA', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Born in the USA in 1965.  Took up with an English lass in Japan in 1994.  Moved to the UK in 1997 obstensibly, for a year.  Became a naturalised citizen in 2002.  My kids are British but also carry US passports. The UK has been good to me.', 'Assimilation;Family;USA', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1429, '1427', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Hong Kong', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I move from Hong Kong to Vancouver to here London! Each place feels like home to me.', 'Hong Kong;Assimilation', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Capital House', 0, 0),
(1430, '1428', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here from the Republic of Ireland in 2005 because my mum don’t like all the rain in Ireland.', 'Family;Ireland', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1431, '1429', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Ethiopia;Netherlands', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born in Ethiopia and I stayed there for a week. Then I moved to Holland and lived there for two years.  Then I moved to London, England.', 'Family;Ethiopia;Netherlands', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1432, '1430', 'Liam Wu', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', NULL, NULL, 'China;Austria', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My family is from China and moved to Austria before I was born. I was born in Austria and at the age of 18 I came to London to find happiness.  But then I went to the Migration Museum and found feels (picture of tears).  Liam Wu', 'Family;China;Austria;Third person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1433, '1431', NULL, NULL, '1960s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'Child Migration', NULL, 'Trinidad and Tobago', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came here at 15 years old from Trinidad and Tobago to get away from an arranged marriage.  In 1963 I have lived in Britain for the past 55 years and hope to live here for the rest of my life.  16/5/18', 'Assimilation;Family;Culture;Trinidad and Tobago', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1434, '1432', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Pakistan', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated to the UK in 2009 from Pakistan.  As a woman of colour, Muslim and non-British citizen, despite my academic and professional accomplishments, the glass ceiling is still too high!', 'Alienation;Ethnicity;Pakistan;Race;Racism;Religion', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1435, '1433', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', 'Love', NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I’ve been living in the UK for 5 years. I’m now 20. London is my home now. I have found the person I love here and will never leave her side.', 'Love;Assimilation', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1436, '1434', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I moved for love and a job to a city I’d never heard about, stayed for university and adventure, and will leave with experiences that I can bring with me forever, and wherever I go.', 'Love;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'x', 0, 0),
(1437, '1435', NULL, NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated to London in 2011 to study for my MA in Special Education.  Now I may need to leave my friends. colleagues, school and children that I teach, post-Brexit.', 'Education;Friends;EU;Politics', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1438, '1436', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Romania', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came here Romania and my dad is mom. We going to London because in ….. ad nt bane Izabela and I spike Romania, English (language very poor).', 'Family;Romania', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'Prendergast Ladywell', 0, 0),
(1439, '1437', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Wanting to study.  I expected a culture of nobility and gentlemen, but landing in Southend Essex I was faced with gang culture and racism.  I moved back to my country but couldn’t recognise the place post-crisis and came back.', 'Ethnicity;Race;Racism;Alienation', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1440, '1438', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Belgium;Pakistan', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Me, my dad, my sister and my brother came from Belgium.  But my mum is from Pakistan, we all moved to England.', 'Family;Belgium;Pakistan', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1441, '1439', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here on the second day of my life from Ireland.  But I’ve spent the rest of my life in England.', 'Ireland', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1442, '1440', 'Daniela', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Portugal', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Hi, my name is Daniela and I’m from Portugal when I was 9 years. Now I have 11 years and so I think that is migrated.', 'Portugal', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1443, '1441', 'Jael. Ola', NULL, '1980s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Nigeria', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated from Nigeria in 1980 to UK, so I am black-British from West-Africa Lagos, Nigeria. Jael. Ola', 'Nigeria', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1444, '1442', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Poland', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born in 2005, Poland.  I moved to England at the age of 2 because my mum wanted to start a life there.  I have been here for 10 years.', 'Family;Poland', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1445, '1443', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Italy', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came from Italy to London 13 years ago to do a university course.  I was supposed to stay for six months but I’m still here! I work as an ESOL teacher with migrants, refugees and asylum speakers in London.', 'Education;Italy', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'x; Being human', 0, 0),
(1446, '1444', NULL, NULL, '1990s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'USA', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to the UK in 1997.  I migrated here from the USA whilst working for British Airways.  I am grateful for the life opportunities and relationships that migrating here has provided!  Long live migration + human diversity!', 'Work;Assimilation;Pride;USA', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', '*', 0, 0),
(1447, '1445', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'New Zealand', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My father was born in Glasgow, Scotland, his family moved to New Zealand when he was very young.  My mother was born in NZ.  I moved to the UK 2 years ago.  Our global movement story continues.', 'Third person;Family;New Zealand', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1448, '1446', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Germany', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I am German and have been living here for 6 years now.  My mother emigrated to the USA when she was 18 – very daring in the 1950s.  She took an ocean liner, as commercial flights weren’t affordable yet.  She returned to Germany 5 years later.  My dad migrated – or rather fled – as a little boy with his mother from East to West Germany, to escape the iron curtain.  I have migrant in my veins.  Since I’ve bee in the UK I have grown a non-profit literature organisation from 1.5 to 6 people.  I’ve created jobs, not taken away any. Brexit makes me angry.', 'Third person;Family;Work;EU;Politics;Wellbeing;Germany', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'Launch Party', 0, 0),
(1449, '1447', 'Asa Christina', NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Commonwealth African country', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to UK 2001 very proud from Commonwealth African country and I was so ashamed on discrimination of race and results of economic refugee instead of a profession.  I had to contribute in health sectors, paid less, worked more. Asa Christina', 'Ethnicity;Race;Racism;Pride;Wellbeing;Alienation;Commonwealth African country', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1450, '1448', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Africa', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I felt British was only dressing up in a religion to cheat Africa.  They don’t even practice it, are more of torture to mind and body.', 'Religion;Wellbeing;Alienation;Africa', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1451, '1449', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'NTC', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here from NTC when I was 5 months old, so I can not remember anything.  I travelled with m two brothers and my parents.', 'Family;NTC', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'Don\'t know where NTC is', 0, 0),
(1452, '1450', 'Sofia', NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Hi! I’m Sofia, came here in 2008 to start my undergrad studies and have been there ever since – here to stay, now a naturalised British citizen.', 'Education', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1453, '1451', 'Pavel', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Moved here in ’14. Will I stay here? Doubtful.  My soul likes to move around.  Now I’m exploring and documenting the secrets of London.  Curious Pavel', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'museum visitor', 0, 0),
(1454, '1452', NULL, NULL, '1930s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Italy', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I with my family migrated from Italy to London in 1936. During 2nd World War – Persecuted as being Italian – When my father was British and with British Army at Dunkirk.', 'War;Family', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1455, '1453', 'Ala B.', NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Lesuire/Retirement', 'Economic', NULL, 'EU', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My great grandfather immigrated from Austria to Brazil.  My mon’s grandfather migrated from Italy to Brazil.  I migrated to the UK as EU citizen because I believed the UK was open minded enough to a 36 year old woman to re-start her life and improve career.  One month before I moved, Brexit was voted and I don’t know if I will be allowed to stay here.  I believe in a global citizenship will exist in the future.  I am not from here, but neither are you. Ala B.', 'Third person;Pride;Work;EU;Politics', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'x', 0, 0),
(1456, '1454', 'Nicole Hansen', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'New Zealand', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I moved to Manchester from New Zealand when I was 11, wearing denim dungarees in the middle of winter! I have since acclimatised.', 'Assimilation;New Zealand', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1457, '1455', NULL, 'Facebook.com/letsnarrowthegap', '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Lesuire/Retirement', NULL, NULL, 'Italy', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I am Italian.  I migrated to London in January 2007.  On the 8th every year since, I celebrate on that day as I consider it as the start of a very lucky journey made of dreams coming true, new opportunities, diverse people, travelling within a city of different cities, continuous discovery.  I feel grateful to life as I could migrate here out of simple dreaming more in my life.  No despair, no poverty, no war.  Just the right passport! I wish the same for everybody.', 'Assimilation;Pride;Wellbeing;Italy', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'x', 0, 0),
(1458, '1456', 'Marcin', NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Hi, my name is Marcin, I came to London in 2004, looking for better living.  I love London since first day.  Thank you.', 'Assimilation', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1459, '1457', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Canada', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I am an accidental migrant: arriving in the UK via Africa.  I had intended to work a few months to fund more travel.  But am still here nearly 18 years later.  The longer I stay the less I think of Canada as ‘home’.', 'Assimilation;Work;Canada;Africa', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1460, '1458', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was not escaping war and violence, but I came to study and improve my life having access to opportunities.  I didn’t have to leave my country. AL MIGRANTS ARE JUST PEOPLE LOOKING FOR A BETTER LIFE.', 'Education', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'x', 0, 0),
(1461, '1459', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Philippines', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents migrated here from the Philippines.', 'Family;Philippines', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1462, '1460', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Afghanistan', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated from Afghanistan with my family because my country is not safe, but I do miss all my cousins back home.', 'Family;War;Afghanistan', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1463, '1461', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to the UK as a baby and will be emigrating out of the UK in the next 12 months – migration comes naturally to humans.', 'Family', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'x', 0, 0),
(1464, '1462', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Eritrea;USA', 'Disc', 'My Migration Story', NULL, 'I became a refugee in 2008, and have been out of my country for the past 10 years.  Now I am American and have especial rights to travel almost all countries in the world and that’s the best.  Thank you!!', 'Assimilation;Eritrea;USA', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'Eritrean-American; An USA Immigration Story', 0, 0),
(1465, '1463', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Lesuire/Retirement', NULL, NULL, 'Spain', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My friends one is next to mine. I was born in Spain.  I came here to make new friends.  Barcelona yeah!', 'Friends;Spain', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1466, '1464', 'Elena', NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Latvia', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Hi, my name is Elena.  I’m Russian speaking, born in Latvia.  My father was Ukranian and now I’m British.  I have moved to UK in 2000 when I was 20 years old and since then it became my home.  It wasn’t always easy but I am grateful for everything.  In 2004 Latvia has jointed the EU and now UK is leaving.  You never know what life will bring.  Enjoy present.', 'Assimilation;Wellbeing;Language;Latvia;EU;Politics', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1467, '1465', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came here more than ten years ago for business. At that time, I wasn’t going to live for long time.  Community try to understand me and government keeps my life.  I have a lot of bad memories in here.  But I studies everyday form not mother country.   (Difficult to make sense out of writing)', 'Alienation;Community;Healthcare', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1468, '1466', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Pakistan;USA', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My mom was born in Pakistan.  Also my dad was born in Amerika.  My dad’s mom was from Pakistan.  When my dad was about 20 years old he came to Pakistan and visited to marry my mom.  Then they both decided go too then my sibling and me were born.  (Difficult to make sense out of writing)', 'Third person;Family;Pakistan;USA', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1469, '1467', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Bangladesh', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born in Bangladesh.  When I was a baby my parents migrated to the UK. I was raised in East London and only been back for few weeks when I was 11.', 'Family;Bangladesh', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', ' 30th June 2017 – Britannia Village School', 0, 0),
(1470, '1468', NULL, NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here because of my father had to come here to work.  I moved here in 2015 and since then I went back to my country only a few times to see my relatives.  I left many things in my country to start a new life.', 'Family;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1471, '1469', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'USA', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born in Chicago.  I moved to London when I was four years old with my mum, dad and sister.  We moved because of my grandparents, as they live in Poland.', 'Family;USA;Netherlands', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1472, '1470', 'Akwaaba – Benvenute', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Italy;Ghana', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here from Italy, where I was a “migrant” as well even though I was born there from Ghanaian parents.  I feel that I am a citizen of the world but I love my countries.', 'Assimilation;Family;Italy;Ghana', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1473, '1471', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Poland', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I moved to England from city in Poland called Gdansk in 2006.  I was twelve years old at that time.', 'Poland', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1474, '1472', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', 'Education', NULL, 'Italy', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'From Italy to study at university.  Moreover, I have migrated from Italy since I was a kid living in different countries and adapting to different cultures and learning new things.', 'Assimilation;Culture;Education;Italy', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1475, '1473', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Spain', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated to London from Spain in 2009.  I’ve now spent enough time in this country to know that I don’t want to live here.  Looking for a new place to migrate to now! I’m very fortunate to be able to move around like that.', 'Wellbeing;Spain', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1476, '1474', NULL, NULL, '1990s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'USA;Nepal', 'Disc', 'My Migration Story', NULL, 'I migrated to the USA with my family from Nepal in 1997 (And now I study in the UK)', 'Family;Education;USA;Nepal', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'launch party; An USA Immigration Story', 0, 0),
(1478, '1476', NULL, NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'Love', NULL, 'Italy;Spain', 'Disc', 'My Migration Story', NULL, 'I’m Italian, but I feel more European than Italian.  I migrated to Sweden after uni, as my Italian office sent me there.  Then I moved to Spain for love.  I married my Romanian wife in Spain.  We moved to the UK in 2012 because of the Spanish economy.  Then Brexit … now I feel I don’t belong here any more.  Not sure where we go next – I speak Italian, English, Spanish, Romanian and French.', 'Alienation;Work;Language;EU;Politics;Italy;Spain', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1479, '1477', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', 'Education', NULL, 'Cyprus', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born in Cyprus.  My mum and my sister as well.  My dad born in Turkey.  He went to Cyprus married my mum.  Me and my sister born, then we come to England when I was 8, for my and my sister’s education. (Thanks for reading)', 'Family;Education;Cyprus', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1480, '1478', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Spain', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated to UK from Spain because we have a very corrupt government.  There’s no job opportunity for young people.  THE SUN IS NOT ALL.', 'Politics;Work;Spain', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1481, '1479', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Italy', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Funny thing, I’m European and from Italy.  I am a migrant but I am the only one to call myself that ‘cause I’m white.  So either I’m a ‘citizen’ or an ‘expat’.  Funny, eh? Not really.', 'Ethnicity;Race;Italy', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1482, '1480', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Latvia;Lithuania', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I’m from Latvia.  I can speak Lithuanian and Russian and England. when I was 5 years old I came to London then to Lithuania and then I’m going to Lithuanian school and then I by 10 years old came to London.  (Difficult to make sense out of writing)', 'Education;Language;Latvia;Lithuania', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', NULL, 0, 0),
(1483, '1481', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I moved to the UK in 2010 to study.  I was lucky enough to find a job quickly and also the love of my life.  And so, I decided to stay.  I love the country and living in London has been wonderful, but not without challenges, always reminding me I am still adjusting. ', 'Education;Assimilation', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'x', 0, 0),
(1484, '1482', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'USA;East Africa', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My parents migrated to the US from East Africa. I decided to continue the legacy and came here to study migration and diasporas.', 'Family;Education;USA;East Africa', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'xx', 0, 0),
(1485, '1483', NULL, NULL, '1980s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Slovenia', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to UK in 1987 as au pair for one month and then stayed.  Later I married an English husband and moved from London to NE Essex.  I am still Slovenian.', 'Education;Slovenia', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'x', 0, 0),
(1486, '1484', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Africa', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here because in Africa iis(is) hopt (hot) and in here is cold.', 'Africa', '', NULL, NULL, 'Yufei', 'Britannia VPS – year 4 30/06/17', 0, 0),
