(1525, '1523', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Italy US ', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My great grandfather was the illegitimate son of a wealthy tourist, either French or English.  He was left in an orphanage in a village in northern Sicily.  Thirty years later he packed his life to find fortune in New York.  He ended up being a valet to Mr Rockefeller in his final days.  He didn’t make a fortune as he hoped, and settled back in Sicily.  Today I have made my way to London to make my dream come true: work in theatre.\n', 'family;third person;work', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1526, '1524', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Probably as minority white Caucasian from a rich country I believed in Britain’s tolerance, openness, compassion …. Perhaps not any more with Brexit.', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
