(1549, '1547', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'France', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here\nI came here because of my love for English and British culture.  I studied it for three years and it felt natural to spend a year in the country.  Once I made some friends, I felt more safe and accepted here and decided to stay.  I started working and becoming an adult here.  I can’t imagine going back to France, and yet I might have to.  Since the Brexit vote I have felt like I don’t really belong anywhere anymore ….. except among my friends.', 'culture;EU;education;friends;language;work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Bessie', NULL, 0, 0),
(1550, '1548', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Australia', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here\nWhen I was one and a half, me and my parents moved from Australia to London – where my brother was born.', 'Australia;family', '', NULL, NULL, 'Bessie', NULL, 0, 0),
(1551, '1549', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, ' migrated here\nI migrated here in September 2009 …. For love! I met Nick in 2008 through a German friend called Christian.  We have been together ever since.  I have always loved London because it is vibrant and alive.', 'love', '', NULL, NULL, 'Bessie', NULL, 0, 0),
