(1562, '1560', NULL, NULL, '1980s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Launch party \nAt least one of my parents migrated here\nMy Dad moved here in the 80s from Ireland.  He hated it, was homesick all the time.  And my mother was alone with 2 children.  But thank you for helping us.', 'family;Ireland;wellbeing', '', NULL, NULL, 'Bessie', 'homesick', 0, 0),
(1563, '1561', 'Amanda Sebeslyer', NULL, '1920s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Hungary;Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here\nMy father was Hungarian and came here to work in 1927.  He built up a company, but could not get statehood and citizenship till 1945 because Britain had a policy of zero immigration.  Later, after he died, I found that many of his family died in the Holocaust.  \nMy mother was born in Ireland before independence, so she was a British citizen and then lost her citizenship, which she got back when she married my foreign father – CRAZY!  Amanda Sebeslyer', 'family;Hungary;Ireland;third-person;work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Bessie', NULL, 0, 0),
(1564, '1562', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here\nAfter my parents got two kids, they moved to England because my dad wanted to get a job here.  Now my parents have five kids, including me.', 'family;war;work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Bessie', NULL, 0, 0),
(1565, '1563', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here\nMy parents and three older siblings moved to London to get away from the war and for better opportunities.', 'family;third-person;war', '', NULL, NULL, 'Bessie', NULL, 0, 0),
