(1573, '1571', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'All of my grandparents married in the UK, East London.  My mother’s parents: grandfather came first and then wrote back to his family to find him a wife, my grandmother then came.  My father’s parents: grandfather was a musrean met grandmother at a local party.', 'Family; Third person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
