(1608, '1606', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Turkey', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents migrated from Turkey due to the fact that Turkey was a country that was hard to make money in, so my mum and dad came.', 'Third Person;Wellbeing;Work', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
