(1625, '1623', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'Economic', NULL, 'Romania ', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here when I was 5 for education and economic purposes.  I was born in Romania', 'education;work', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1626, '1624', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Austria;Canada;Poland', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born in Poland, lived in Austria as a refugee, grew up in Canada and now study here', 'culture;education', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1627, '1625', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Vietnam', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I’m from a Vietnamese refugee family who left by boat after the fall of Saigon.  They made it to Australia where I was born.  I moved here 7 years agol.', 'Culture', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1628, '1626', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Greece', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Born in Greece, I came here for 1st time back in 2009, for my MSc.  I moved back to my country for 1 year and since 2011 I am working in London.  Hope to go back someday.', 'Education;work', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1629, '1627', 'Alexandria', NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Egypt', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My parents migrated to UK in 1957 – I was six, from Alexandria, Egypt.  Ismat', 'Family', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1630, '1628', NULL, NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here on the 4th July 2019 with my parents so they got a better life and for my education.', 'education;family;wellbeing', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1631, '1629', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Israel', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born in Israel in its early days.  Came here as a young child.', 'Culture', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1632, '1630', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was nearly 5 years old when I migrated to London to be with my mother and father.  I didn’t know them, I missed my grandmother.  My book of poems celebrated her.\n', 'culture;family;Language', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1633, '1631', NULL, NULL, '1980s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I started several companies and they provide lots of work for many people, 1983 to present\n', 'community;work', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1634, '1632', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'New Zeland', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here from New Zealand when I was 7.  We stayed here for 8 years and then returned to NZ.  Now I am back!', 'family;New Zeland', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1635, '1633', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Denmark', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Because of family as when I lived in Denmark there were not a lot of family and we were very lonely.  Also education, the system was very different in a bad way.  Also where I lived it was very racist.', 'Culture;Education;Family;Race;Racism', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1636, '1634', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Italy', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'No Brexit!\nWe came from Vienna to work here as teachers.  It doesn’t really feel like migration to us since we live in a globalised world without kept borders which makes it feel more like a global community to us.\n', 'Culture;Education;politics;work', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1637, '1635', NULL, NULL, '1960s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'China;Malaysia', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I’m Chinese and came here from Malaysia in 1963 to do a postgraduate degree.  I married an Englishman with Polish and Swiss ancestry.  I completed my doctorate and taught at London University.  My granddaughter’s father is from Venezuela.  London has been my home for over 50 years.\n', 'Culture;education;family;work', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1638, '1636', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Greece;Poland;Romania', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My mum and dad met in Greece and that was where I was born.  My mum is from Poland and my dad is from Romania.  Me and my family came here when I was 9 and I’ve lived in London ever since.', 'culture;family;third person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1639, '1637', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Brazil', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My parents met in Brazil working for an NGO.  When I was about 1 we moved back to London from beautiful Olinda.  I love both places.', 'culture;family;third person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1640, '1638', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', NULL, NULL, 'India', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here from India after I got married to a British national.  It was very difficult to leave all my family back in India and make a new life here', 'Assimilation;culture;Family', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1641, '1639', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Zimbabwe', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated to the UK from Zimbabwe in December 2000 when I was 15.  Life here was very too different to go back home and it still is in a lot of ways.  16 years late this now home but can’t say I feel like I truly belong.  That said I am grateful for all the opportunities I have had being here.', 'Alienation;Assimilation', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1642, '1640', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'India', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I moved to the UK when I was 4 years old from India.  We woke up at 4am with my mum hurriedly dressing me and my family surrounded, slightly sad.  20 hours later and a first  plane ride I found myself in the chilly UK.', 'Alienation;culture;family', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1643, '1641', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My Mum, siblings and I migrated here in hope for a better education.  This was one of the best decisions ever made, because I now have a lot of friends and freedom to do what I want and not be judged for it.', 'Education;Family;Friends;Wellbeing', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1644, '1642', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Italy', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was 8 when I came to England and had to leave all my friends behind.  I came from Italy and didn’t speak any English.  I was also bullied until I learned English.', 'Alienation;Friends;Language', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1645, '1643', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Afghanistan', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Hi! My Dad migrated to the UK in the early 2000’s and I migrated here when I was 2 with my sister and mum.  My Dad chose to move to the UK from Afghanistan as there was conflict there and he wanted us to have a better future (i.e., education).', 'education;family;wellbeing', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(1646, '1644', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Afghanistan;Belgium', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My parents migrated throughout Europe, from Afghanistan to Belgium, then I was born there and 6 years later I moved to London. ', 'Family', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0);
