(1689, '1687', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'France Germany', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My great grandparents – German and French met during the first world war in the UK where they settled. The other side of my family are all adopted – so we’re still working it out.\n', 'Family;third person', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
