(1777, '1775', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'Forced Migration/Enslavement', NULL, 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandparents migrated to London from Ireland during the Second World War, they still live here.', 'Family;Ireland;war;third person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(1778, '1776', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Jamaica', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandparents migrated here around the 1930-40s from Jamaica. They travelled on Windrush boat.', 'Family;Jamaica;third person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(1779, '1777', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'British Gypsy', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandmother was a British Gypsy. She said if the Nazis got here I would not be here. “Always remember citizenship is contingent”', 'Family;British Gypys;genocide', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', 'taken for HMD', 0, 0),
(1780, '1778', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'St.Lucia', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandparents migrated here from St. Lucia to England to have my mum.', 'Family;St.Lucia;third person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(1781, '1779', NULL, NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Germany', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandma’s mum went to England with her step-brother, but not with her. She stayed with her granny and great-aunt, in Germany. In the late 50s she moved to England and got married. Shortly after the marriage she had a son, my uncle.', 'Family;Germany;friends', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(1782, '1780', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandfather, [redacted], came to the UK in the 30’s, and trained as a doctor, running a GP practice in Sheffield.', 'Family;third person;work', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Rajendra Lal Shrivastava', 0, 0),
(1783, '1781', NULL, NULL, '1990s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My mum sold her wedding ring to pay for flights to the UK for me, my sister and her when I was 1 year old, in 1996.', 'family;third person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(1784, '1782', 'cynthia', 'cig38@hotmail.com', NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents migrated here when Mum fell pregnant with me. My conception changed the path of their lives.', 'Family;third person;friends', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(1785, '1783', 'Emma Leaver', 'emmaleaver@gmail.com', NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I have dual nationality, arriving from Melbourne in 2012. I love London’s diversity and cultural melting pot. Bot no one expects you to feel like an immigrant with a British passport They also assume you are always OK with having your accent, traditions, etc, mocked, because you’re “basically the same anyway”. I was only going to stay for a couple of years, love keeps me here. I’m not Australian, I’m not British, I am a Londoner.', 'Australia;friends;culture;community;assimilation;alienation', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(1786, '1784', 'cynthia', 'cig38@hotmail.com', '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here at age 11 years.  Mine was not a happy story.  Am still trying to go back home.\n', 'alienation', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(1787, '1785', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Nigeria', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My mum and dad came to Italy from Nigeria during the 90’s. They later gave birth to me and years later I came to London with my mum, dad, beautiful granny and sisters.', 'Family;third person;Nigeria;Italy', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(1788, '1786', NULL, NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My father emigrated from the UK to then Southern Rhodesia as part of the Fairbridge Migration Scheme in 1952 (he was 11). How sad that it was ok to send children alone half way across the world without their parents. Many of the children on the scheme were very badly treated, suffering abuse of all kinds.', 'Family;race;alienation;third person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(1789, '1787', NULL, 'Chloe', NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Australia', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'Australia – my dad left Australia 15 years ago. He met my mummy and now lives here. Chloe age 4.', 'Family;Australia;third person;friends', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', 'age 4', 0, 0),
(1790, '1788', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'Several members of my family emigrated to the USA.  On of them told “an amended version of the truth” …. to be able to stay there. We’ve all benefited from that chance that was taken.  I never forget that.\n', 'Family:USA;third person;assimilation', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(1791, '1789', NULL, NULL, '1940s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'India', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'Both maternal grandparents (Caucasian) were the first to return from India in the 1940s. Their accents and culture meant they felt like outsiders in their ‘home country’. We can’t trace far enough back to find out who was the first generation to go out to India in the first place.', 'Family;Caucas;India;alienation;wellbeing', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(1792, '1790', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My Dad came here from Ireland when he was 15 with nothing but his suitcase. He worked a few jobs before becoming a postman working his way up to being a manager. My Nan & Grandad came here from Poland and Spain. My grandad was a tailor in the second war. My mother was Jewish and my dad was Catholic. To look at me you wouldn’t think anything other than white British.', 'family;Ireland;Spain;Poland;work;assimilation;genocide;war', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', 'taken for HMD', 0, 0),
(1793, '1791', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', NULL, NULL, 'India', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My dad’s parents migrated from India to Zambia and then from Zambia to the UK in 1978. They came with my dad and his 3 siblings. My dad was still a teenage and my mum came here in the late 80s to get married to my dad. I am 1 of 6 siblings and I am 17 years old.', 'Family;india;Zambia;friends;third person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(1794, '1792', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Italy', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My grandmother (paternal) is of Romani-Gypsy heritage. They migrated to Britain in the 1800s. My great grandfather (maternal) emigrated from Florence.', 'Family;third person;Italy;Romani-Gypsy;religion', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', 'Launch party', 0, 0),
(1795, '1793', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'USA,Austria', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'Although there are not many migrants in my family to my knowledge, my brother has moved away to work and live in America, other relatives have moved and settled in Austria, and I plan to move away myself later this year before I lose my European citizenship!', 'Family;USA,Austria,work;assimilation', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(1796, '1794', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'New Zealand', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My father left the UK at age 12 and moved with his family to NZ.', 'Family;New Zealand;third person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', 'Launch party', 0, 0),
