(1821, '1819', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Cyprus', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents were economic migrants. My parents were Greek speaking Cypriots who came here after WW2. Dad fought in the Cyprus regiment for the war in Egypt and Palestine. They ran a fish and chip shop and employed 4 people before they retired. They had 4 children and all of us have led productive lives in the UK.', 'Family;cyprus;third person;work;friends;assimilation', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
