(1875, '1873', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', NULL, NULL, 'French Guyana;Dominicana', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My father migrated from French Guyana to Domenica and met my mother there. They both came and live and London. I am a Londoner of Caribbean origin.', 'Family;French Guyana;Dominicana;third person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
