(1877, '1875', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Slovakia', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Mum migrated here, 100 pounds in her pocket. Now has a highly successful business and takes us (me and my brother) on 5 star holidays. Came from impovished past, communist Slovakia.', 'Family;Slovakia;assimilation;work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
