(1883, '1881', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Lebanon', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents got married in Lebanon. Then my dad immigrated from Lebanon to England. About 2 weeks later, my mum came to England as well.', 'Family;Lebanon;friends;third person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
