(1885, '1883', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Russia;USA', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mum was born in Seattle, America, and my dad was born in St Petersburg, Russia.  My dad moved to Boston when he was 11, then here, and my mum later moved to London.', 'Family;USA;Russia;third person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
