(1976, '1974', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Denmark', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'To my knowledge, all my family consists of Danes. We have a long history of Danes without any migrants. I’m white, with red hair and have blue eyes.', 'Family;Denmark;third person;culture', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
