(1987, '1984', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Colombia', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'I am from Colombia, there are no migrants in my family, to my knowledge, until now. I became the first migrant in my family and I just married a Greek guy.', 'Family;Colombia', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
