(2080, '2075', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'New Zealand;Malta', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My great great grandparents on my mother’s side emigrated to New Zealand. One of their sons joined the NZ Navy, worked in Egypt, and traveled to many places round the globe. He settled in Malta. His daughter came to the UK so that is why I am here. I recently contacted my NZ cousin who I never knew I had. (Migration Museum is a brilliant project- long may it continue).', 'Europe;Family;Malta;New Zealand;Oceania', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2081, '2076', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Germany', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'There are no immigrants in my family that I know of, but my uncle moved to Germany, for work I think, and married and had children there.', 'Europe;Family;Germany;Thrid person;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Boya', NULL, 0, 0),
(2083, '2078', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'Local migration stories from S London i.e. The Latin American community in Elephant+Castle or Vietnamese community in Deptford etc. Any info on disabled immigration/emigration?', 'Asia;Community;Culture;North America;South America;Vietnam', '', NULL, NULL, 'Boya', NULL, 0, 0),
(2084, '2079', 'Nadia', NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'Draw and get to take pictures with Carabean people. Thank you from Nadia. <3 xoxoxo', 'South America', '', NULL, NULL, 'Boya', NULL, 0, 0),
(2085, '2080', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'No details', 'No details', 'Norway', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I moved to London at the age of 9. My dad got a job offer he couldn’t refuse and moved my family from Oslo to Wimbledon. Norway- England.', 'Europe;Family;Norway;Work', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2086, '2081', '', NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Norway;Scotland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandmother moved here from Trondheim, Norway in 1950\'s. My grandad was Scottish but spoke Norsk as he had fought there in WW2. Despite being born here, my mother says she didn’t feel British till she married a Brit. We go to a Norwegian language Church in Rotherhithe.', 'Alienation;Europe;Family;Norway;Religion;Thrid person;War', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2087, '2082', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'To get a better education.', 'Education', '', NULL, NULL, 'Boya', NULL, 0, 0),
(2088, '2083', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'Lobbying to change the vocabulary associated with moving! Expat. Immigrant. Explorer. Traveller. Huran x', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Boya', NULL, 0, 0),
(2089, '2084', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Jamaica', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grannie and grandpa moved here separately from Jamaica in the windrush. One became a nurse, one a postmaster, but they both became fully embedded in the London black culture.', 'Cultrue;Empire;Family;Jamaica;South America;Thrid person;Work', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2090, '2085', '', NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Afghanistan', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My father came here from Afghanistan in the early 2000\'s. We came here in 2007. 14 years of living in this country made me realise the language and culture has become part of me.', 'Afghanistan;Asia;Culture;Language;Family', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2091, '2086', '', NULL, '1990s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Guyana', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My nana migrated here from Guyana in the 90\'s.', 'Family;Guyana;South America', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'grandparent migrated', 0, 0),
(2092, '2087', '', NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', 'No details', 'No details', 'China', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to London from China in 2000, when I was 19. I met my husband who is also from China. and we now have a 6 year old daughter. London is our home.', 'Asia;China;Family', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2093, '2088', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My stepfather got a job and we wanted a change. We moved to London for a year, but we ended up staying here.', 'Family;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Boya', NULL, 0, 0),
(2094, '2089', 'Jonathan NZ', NULL, '1890s', 'Image', 'Emigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'India;New Zealand', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My great grandparents, from Shoreditch in London, emigrated initially to India, returned to London, then emigrated to New Zealand at the turn of the century 1800/1900\'s. They wanted to escape the life that they had in east London and the low social standing. ', 'Asia;Family;India;New Zealand;Oceania;Thrid person;Wellbeing', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2095, '2090', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Emigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'USA', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My family left Selby, England and settled in the state of Florida, United States. We can track the family to the Abbey in Selby, most of my family stayed.', 'Family;North America;ReligionUSA;', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2096, '2091', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Italy;Jamaica', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandad came from Jamaica and my grandma came from Italy.', 'Family;Europe;Italy;Jamaica;South America;Thrid person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Boya', NULL, 0, 0),
(2097, '2092', 'Salman', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Afghanistan', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Afghanistan taken over by taliban.', 'Afghanistan;Asia;Politics;Religion;War', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2098, '2093', '', NULL, '1930s', 'Image', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Canada', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'My mum and her sisters were adopted. Their adoptive parents migrated to Canada but they could not go because the children were adopted. This was the 1930\'s.', 'Canada;Family;North America;Thrid person', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2099, '2094', '', NULL, '1930s', 'Image', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Canada', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'My husband’s father had an apartment and papers to migrated to Canada with his family. They never showed up at the appointed time.', 'Canada;Family;North America;Thrid person', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2100, '2095', '', NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Jamaica', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandparents came here in the 1950’s. My grandad worked on the railway. They came from Jamaica. They lived in New Cross.', 'Family;Jamaica;South America;Thrid person;Work', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2101, '2096', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, '… by choice. It’s a great privilege. I’m very happy here, and very grateful.', 'Pride', '', NULL, NULL, 'Boya', NULL, 0, 0),
(2102, '2097', '', NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'Love', 'No details', 'Israel;Norway', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I met a girl in the Amazons travelling - I wanted to do a masters back home in Norway but did so in London instead as she lived there (but herself israeli). She is now my wife and I have lived in London for 21 years.', 'Asia;Education;Europe;Family;Israel;Norway', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2103, '2098', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Brazil', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mom migrated here from Brazil.', 'Family;Brazil;South America', '', NULL, NULL, 'Boya', NULL, 0, 0),
(2104, '2099', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'No details', 'No details', 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'From Derry, Ireland. I was coming over to study, but I didn’t go back because I didn’t want to live in a community driven by sectarian violence. I moved to London after uni because I knew no one would ask my religion or social class', 'Class;Ireland;Europe;Politics;Pride;Religion', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2105, '2100', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'Want to see more stoires of migration.', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Boya', NULL, 0, 0),
(2156, '2151', '', NULL, '1990s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'Child Migration', 'No details', 'Afghanistan', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came with my family as a refugee. We were fleeing the talibans as we were a Shia branch of muslims from Hazera tribe. I left in 1997 when the talibans took Kabul for the first time. I didn’t really understand until I was 9 years old.', 'Afganistan;Ethnicity;Family;Religion;War', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2157, '2152', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Albania;Macedonia;North Macedonia', 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'More artefacts from Macedonia and Albania.', 'Albania;Culture;Macedonia;North Macedonia', '', NULL, NULL, 'Kirill', NULL, 0, 0),
(2158, '2153', '', NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'Economic', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Back in 2016 I had decided to come to London to study theatre. Now (in 2021??), I have a MA in Acting and am trying to start my career.', 'Education;Work', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2159, '2154', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'Please can we have a story disc for people who move between two countries - here and abroad.(Sam?)', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Kirill', NULL, 0, 0),
(2160, '2155', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'No details', 'No details', 'Dominica', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, '2 of My grandparents came to the UK from Dominica which is a small island in the Caribbean.They were part of the windrush generation, but all I know is they experienced some prejudice and challenges. They also became quite english (supporting Arsenal to this day) and found work as a bus driver and policeman. They moved back when I was little, but I still call them every 2 weeks.', 'Assimilation;Dominica;Racism;Third Person;Work', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Windrush', 0, 0),
(2161, '2156', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'Caribbean man (institutionalise ?) due to being misunderstood (Drarent Park?).', 'Assimilation', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Probably referring to Darenth Park Hospital, a mental health institution near Dartford which was shut in 1988. Its catchment area included much of south-east London and Kent. ', 0, 0),
(2162, '2157', 'Enrique', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I emigrate (immigrate?) to have a better future.', 'LIfestyle', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2163, '2158', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated with my wife and daughter to the UK to study. Originally, my wife was from the UK and we met in Australia. We have now permanently settled.\r\n', 'Education;Family;', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2164, '2159', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My dad migrated here first. He worked as a kitchen porter to save enough money to bring the rest of us here afterwards. He still washes dishes, but in his own shop now.\r\n\r\n', 'Work', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 1, 5),
(2165, '2160', '', NULL, '1920s', 'Image', 'Emigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My great grandmother emigrated from the UK in 1921. She came alone as a single woman with a large travel trunk + settled permanently.', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2166, '2161', '', NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', 'No details', 'No details', 'Kenya', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to England at the age of 16 from Kenya. I have now lived in England for 23 years and feel that both countries are home.\r\n', 'Africa; Teenager;Home', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2167, '2162', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Austria', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I am of Colombian origin (Father) and my mother is from the UK but was born in Austria. I could not go to Colombia due to political problems.\r\n', 'Latin America;Europe;Politics ', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2168, '2163', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Emigration', 'Love', 'No details', 'No details', 'Brazil;Netherlands;Sweden ', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My father moved to Brazil from Sweden in his early 30\'s. He then met my mom and now both live in the Netherlands.\r\n', 'Latin America;Europe;Love', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Not emigrated from the UK ', 0, 0),
(2169, '2164', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My father was treated really poorly, had to live in really cramped conditions, and share a room with several strangers - the government had promised him individual accommodations. He was spat on, sworn at, and refused service in some places.', 'Discrimination; Racisim;Poor living conditions', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2170, '2165', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Forced Migration/Enslavement', 'No details', 'No details', 'Denmark;Somalia', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'My parents migrated from Somalia to Denmark to escape the civil war. After being treated with hostility, facing racism and Islamophobia, they moved to London to raise a family.', 'Africa;Civil War; Hostility;Racism;Islamophobia', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Wrong disc type used, should have been \'At least one of my parents migrated here\'', 0, 0),
(2171, '2166', NULL, NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Emigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Canada', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My parents and younger sister moved to Canada 6 years ago.\r\n\n', 'Family;North America; Emigration', '', NULL, NULL, 'Farhana', NULL, 0, 0),
(2172, '2167', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'India', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandma and grandpa migrated from India to England :)', 'Asia', '', NULL, NULL, 'Farhana', NULL, 0, 0),
(2173, '2168', '', NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Hi, my mother came over in the 50\'s from Ireland, Tipperary, R. A. Sweeney. She struggled to find somewhere to live. Her Irish family stayed over there, except for one niece. Have a nice day.', 'Europe;Struggle', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2174, '2169', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Forced Migration/Enslavement', 'No details', 'No details', 'Sri Lanka', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Both of my parents migrated here from Sri Lanka, due to wars there. They came here seeking more opportunities and a better lifestyle.', 'Asia;War;Better Lifestyle;Oppurtunities', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2175, '2170', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Sri Lanka', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Both of my parents migrated here from Sri Lanka, due to wars there. They came here seeking more opportunities and a better lifestyle.', 'Asia; Oppurtunities; Extended Family', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2176, '2171', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'Acknowledgement that migration has a lot of downsides: atomization, rootlessness, loss of contact with friends, relatives, and so much, much more.', 'Alienation;Culture;Family;Wellbeing', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2177, '2172', 'Harriet', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'No details', 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'Potentially great (great) grandparents migrated here from Ireland during the potato famine. My mom\'s surname was literally “Irish” before she married.', 'Empire;Family;Genocide', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2178, '2173', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'No details', 'No details', 'Norway', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My whole family migrated here from Norway because my mom got a job. We are moving back in 9 days. We only wanted to stay in the UK for a year.', 'Family;Norway;Work', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2179, '2174', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mum migrated to the UK after marrying my dad because they both wanted a better lifestyle.', 'Family', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2180, '2175', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My dad migrated here from Morocco, Casablanca.', 'Family;Morocco', '', NULL, NULL, 'Kirill', NULL, 0, 0),
(2181, '2176', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'No details', 'Cuba;USA', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mum moved here from the U.S after she married my father. All of her family in the U.S are Cuban, and her mothers generation had all fled Cuba for Miami after the revolution.', 'Cuba;Family;Politics;USA', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2182, '2177', '', NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Barbados', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandparents migrated here from Barbados in the fifties. They shared rooms with multiple tenants as accommodation was hard to come by. Racism was blatant and quite the norm.', 'Barbados;Racism', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2183, '2178', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'No details', 'No details', 'India;Kenya;Pakistan', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My Punjabi grandparents migrated to Kenya from India + Pakistan to work on the railways, then they came to London to give a better life to my dad. I am proud to be Kenyan Punjabi.', 'Empire;Family;India;Kenya;Pakistan;Pride;Work', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2184, '2179', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'Child Migration', 'Netherlands;Somalia', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'At the age of 6, I immigrated to the UK from the Netherlands, like many other Somali families. My mother decided that moving to the UK would give us more opportunities and a better life.', 'Family;Netherlands;Somalia', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2185, '2180', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'To help a friend who needed me for 3 weeks. It has been 11 months this month that I have been here. Gladly, don\'t get me wrong. There have been hard days, but I\'ve learnt life the best way here. I would not redo a bit. Thanks London. Hard but fair (master??) Be kind and grateful for our presence!', 'Friends;UK;Wellbeing', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2186, '2181', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'More interactive stories, videos, historic photos, theatre.', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2187, '2182', 'Camila', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'Economic', 'No details', 'Colombia', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I immigrated from Colombia for a better future, because in London there are more opportunities than in my home country. That\'s why I came to study. ', 'Colombia;Education', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Wrong disc type. Originally transcribed as ', 0, 0),
(2188, '2183', 'Saman ', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'No details', 'No details', 'Iran', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Bad government in Iran and to make a good future.', 'Iran;Politics', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2189, '2184', '', NULL, '1970s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'No details', 'No details', 'Uganda', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My father\'s side of the family moved to the UK as refugees from Idi Amin\'s Uganda in 1972. They landed in Stansted and were then resettled in Luton. He became high sheriff of Bedfordshire in 2017 and the focus this year was community cohesion.', 'Assimilation;Politics;Uganda;UK;Work', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 1, 0),
(2190, '2185', '', NULL, '1990s', 'Image', 'No details', 'Love', 'No details', 'No details', 'USA', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My mother emigrated from the UK to the U.S in 1990 to be with my father, who is American. His people emigrated from Europe in the 1800\'s. Now I have immigrated back here to the UK.', 'Family;UK;USA', '', '', NULL, NULL, '1990s + 1880s', 0, 0),
(2191, '2186', 'Daran Mitchelle', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Ivory Coast ', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents came from Ivory Coast.', 'Family;Ivory Coast;South Africa ', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2192, '2187', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'To escape war.', 'War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', NULL, 0, 0),
(2193, '2188', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'I would love to see more diary entries, and more stories from young people/children.', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2194, '2189', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My cousins, who I played with often when growing up, migrated here. I remember meeting them and being introduced when they first arrived.', 'Family', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Wrong disc: cousins migrated to UK', 0, 0),
(2195, '2190', '', NULL, '1960s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'No details', 'No details', 'Nigeria', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'To study Arabic at SOAS in 1966 from Nigeria.', 'Education;Language;Nigeria', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Should be ', 0, 0),
(2196, '2191', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Canada', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to the U.K over 12 years ago to teach. I’m now settled in London but no longer teaching. Originally from Canada with a mom from the U.K.', 'Assimilation;Canada;Education;Empire;Family;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', NULL, 0, 0),
(2197, '2192', '', NULL, '1970s', 'Image', 'No details', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'Education', 'No details', 'Canada;Hong Kong;Kenya;Northern Ireland;Oman;Saudi Arabia;', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I am the result of a 19th century/early 20th century migration from the Portuguese colony of Goa to British East Africa. Born in Kenya, I came to London in 1971. I was a refugee and was stateless for 9 years, a process that almost destroyed me. I left to work in Saudi Arabia in 1981 and, after 3 years, to Oman. I then returned and studied in Northern Ireland. After 1990, I was an active member of Lewisham;s LGBTQ scene and then in HIV services. I left for Canada in 2014 and now live in Hong Kong.', 'Canada;Community;Education;Empire;Healthcare;Hong Kong;India;Kenya;LGBT;Northern Ireland;Politics;Oman;Saudi Arabia;War;Wellbeing', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Migrated to UK for 2nd time in 1980s', 0, 0),
(2198, '2193', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'I love all the video and audio accessibility, but the reading parts were quite difficult for my dyslexia, so if it is possible to have audio options for the physical reading parts.', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2199, '2194', '', NULL, '1960s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'No details', 'No details', 'Kenya ', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My dad’s family first migrated to Kenya, and then Leicester, UK in the 1960\'s. They changed the family name to be successful and we now have a large family here.', 'Family;Kenya;South Africa;UK;Leicester;Work ', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2200, '2195', 'Evelin', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'No details', 'No details', 'Dominican Republic', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My name is Evelin. I came from Dominican Republic to have a better future.', 'Dominican Republic;North America', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2201, '2196', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Pakistan', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandparents migrated to the UK after my grandad went back to Pakistan on a holiday and ended up passing away :(. My grandma had to raise her 7 kids alone. She was separated from 4 of her kids as they didn’t get a visa to come to the UK, so they had to raise themselves.', 'Asia;Family;Pakistan;Third person', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 1, 0),
(2202, '2197', NULL, NULL, '1970s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Vietnam', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came from Hong Gai in Vietnam in 1979 when I was 3 years old! Tuan.', 'Asia;Vietnam', '', NULL, NULL, 'Boya', NULL, 0, 0),
(2203, '2198', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'I would love to see the migration museum housed in a permanent gallery and recognised as the essential part of our National Arts + Heritage sector that it is!', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Boya', NULL, 0, 0),
(2204, '2199', '', NULL, '1990s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Yugoslavia', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mother moved to the UK to join her father, who came from Yugoslavia after WW2. My father moved in the early 90\'s to join his mother. Just before the outbreak of civil war, they met at a folk dance and settled in Telford - which still has a strong Yugoslav diaspora more on this!', 'Europe;Family;Thrid Person;War;Yugoslavia;', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2205, '2200', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'I would like to see more about the Irish Diaspora.', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Boya', NULL, 0, 0),
(2206, '2201', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, 'Lebanon', NULL, 'I migrated here', NULL, 'First, I migrated from my country to Lebanon for 7 years and then to London for 3 years. Just because of the war, I lost 7 years without studying after they destroyed my house and my country. I came here to study.', 'Education; Lebanon; War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2207, '2202', 'G.nia', 'wgnia@hotmail.com', NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'I have an old video called “Motherland” and I also write poems.', 'Culture;Family;Language', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2208, '2203', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', NULL, NULL, 'Turkey', NULL, 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My dad is English but grew up in various RAF houses and eventually lived in Turkey as an adult, where he met my mom. They moved here, then to Turkey (where I was born) then to the UAE (where I grew up). I am a British citizens but I did not live here until I was 18.', 'Family; Turkey', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2209, '2204', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Poland', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mom lived in Poland when she was little. She came here to study and she still lives here now.', 'Education; Family; Poland', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2210, '2205', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'I emigrated for a better future which is why I came to this country and to London. I have more study and work opportunities than in my country.', 'Education; Family; Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2211, '2206', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration', 'Love', NULL, NULL, 'Jamaica;Tanzania', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mum came from Jamaica and my dad came from Tanzania. I would not be here without migration!', 'Family; Jamaica; Tanzania', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2212, '2207', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'More rooms that have audio options.', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2213, '2208', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'More stories and information about more recent and modern migration.', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2214, '2209', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Oman', NULL, 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated from Oman to the UK in 2006 for higher education, been in different UK cities but mostly in London. After 15 years, I am planning to emigrate to Pakistan where my origins are to take care of my father, might visit UK though.', 'Education; Family; Oman', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2215, '2210', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Pakistan', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My father came here from Pakistan in the 90s. I was born in 1957. Schools in those days said if I learnt Urdu my English would suffer! Sadly, at 64, I can speak it so have grown up denied this part of me, racism permeates all as part of identity.', 'Family; Language; Pakistan', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2216, '2211', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I emigrated to have a better future.', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2217, '2212', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Niue', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'From the island of Niue.', 'Family; Niue', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2218, '2213', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Forced Migration/Enslavement', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'I migrated here', NULL, 'To escape war and oppression from the Talibani invasion, to have more safety.', 'War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2219, '2214', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Netherlands', NULL, 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'Both my parents (British) emigrated to the Netherlands for my mother’s job. My mom and my sister have since migrated back. I came back for university and my father travels between the two countries.', 'Education; Family; Netherlands; Third person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2220, '2215', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Bangladesh', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandad migrated to the UK with his family when my mum was 11 years old. Then my mom went back to Bangladesh to get married at 16 and my dad migrated here too. Happily ever after :)', 'Bangladesh; Family; Third person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2221, '2216', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Kenya;Pakistan', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mom is a Kenyan Pakistani that migrated to London to create a better life for her kids that they have everything but is proud to be African-Punjabi.', 'Africa; Culture; Family; Kenya; Pakistan; Third person; ', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2222, '2217', NULL, NULL, '1970s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandparents moved here in the 1970s. They came to Bristol and converted an old psychiatric home into an eight-bedroom house. Love those guys!', 'Family', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2223, '2218', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ireland', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My father was adopted from Ireland from a couple who did not want a baby. Later on, he changed his name to whom it was before the adoption because of legal issues that would often grant him a level of anonymity.', 'Family; Ireland', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2224, '2219', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Australia', NULL, 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I moved here from Sydney, Australia for work. Found love and a happy life in SE London. Built a family and feel part of an amazing community here.', 'Australia; Community; Family; Third person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2225, '2220', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Uganda', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mom came to England at the age of 12 because of war. My mom came from Uganda.', 'Family; Uganda; War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2226, '2221', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I emigrated to have a better future.', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `stories` (`id`, `Story_Number`, `Name_of_ppt`, `Contact_details`, `Date_of_story`, `Story_Format`, `Migration_Category`, `Migration_Sub-Category`, `Migration_Sub-Category1`, `Migration_Sub-Category2`, `Country`, `Exhibition`, `Disc_Type`, `Other_Interactive_Format`, `Story`, `Keywords`, `AI_Keywords`, `Link_to_transcript_file`, `Link_to_raw_data_audio_video_image`, `Completed_by`, `Notes`, `reviewed`, `votes`) VALUES
(2227, '2222', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Bangladesh', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Both my parents came from Sylhet, Bangladesh. Most Bangladeshis in the UK are from this region. My dad worked in restaurants before joining the British Rail. My mum worked in a textiles factory.', 'Bangladesh; Family; Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2228, '2223', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Jamaica', NULL, 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My grandpa and grandma emigrated from Jamaica to London for a better life. But they have children in Jamaica and London.', 'Family; Jamaica; Third person; Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2229, '2224', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Jamaica', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Actually, both my parents came from Jamaica. My maternal grandmother was already here and sent for her daughter once she was settled. My father left Jamaica to seek better work prospects. When he became ill he came back there as he wanted to die in his homeland.', 'Family; Jamaica; Third person; Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2230, '2225', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Jamaica', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'All of my grandparents came from Jamaica to the UK for a better life and money.', 'Family; Jamaica; Third person; Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2231, '2226', 'Yanibel', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Dominican Republic', NULL, 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My name is Yanibel. I came from Dominican Republic to have a better future.', 'Dominican Republic', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2232, '2227', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Forced Migration/Enslavement', NULL, NULL, 'India;Kenya', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandad migrated from India to Kenya (20 years) back to India due to gangs. Then he moved to the UK when my dad was 12. Dad went to India to get married and came back here. The rest is history.', 'Family; India; Kenya; Politics', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2233, '2228', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'Stories about coming back to the UK and the displacement you feel. Stories from South-East Asia and those who went there during WW2. (Taiwan gold mines)', 'Taiwan', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2234, '2229', NULL, NULL, '1960s', 'Image', 'Emigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Canada', NULL, 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My great uncles, David and Terry emigrated to Canada in the 1960s. Living in Calgary and Toronto.', 'Canada; Family', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2235, '2230', NULL, NULL, '1850s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Ireland', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My great-great grandparents came to Wales during the potato famine. I know that they lived in County Cork and they were working on ships there.', 'Family; Ireland; Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2236, '2231', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Forced Migration/Enslavement', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Me and my mom and siblings migrated here for safety, escaping the government because my mom is a politician and my dad as well.', 'Family; Politics', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2237, '2232', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'Regional UK history of migration, Asian history of migration, female livelihood in WW2, conversations with older generations before they are lost (rural)', 'Asia', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2238, '2233', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My dad migrated to the UK so my siblings would not be without migration. Likewise with my baby boy - product of migration.', 'Family', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2239, '2234', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', NULL, NULL, 'Australia', NULL, 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here from Australia to live with my partner who is Swedish. We love London’s vibrancy and diversity.', 'Australia; Celebration; Culture; Family; Sweden', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2240, '2235', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Germany', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mom Yanniyna moved to England 4 years ago from Germany.', 'Family; Germany', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2241, '2236', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Forced Migration/Enslavement', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, 'Hong Kong', NULL, 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Fled Hong Kong for fear of political prosecution. Thanks to the UK for letting me take shelter here.', 'Hong Kong; Politics', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2242, '2237', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'New Zealand', NULL, 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My parents decided to emigrate to New Zealand when I was 5 and my sister was 3. This museum brought back a lot of memories. I think of myself as a N. Z. Londoner now.', 'Family; New Zealand', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2243, '2238', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jamaica', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Both of my parents migrated here from Jamaica. My father told us stories of how difficult it was back then. They stuck together and overcame adversity.', 'Family; Jamaica; Racism', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2244, '2239', NULL, NULL, '1990s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Afghanistan', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My dad moved to London in 1995 (from Afghanistan).', 'Afghanistan; Family', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2245, '2240', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Ireland', NULL, 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I moved from Southern Ireland for the opportunities London offered. Then I met my now wife who is from Southampton and have settled here to raise 2 children who sound more like Peppa pig, that’s me!', 'Family; Ireland; Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2246, '2241', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Lithuania', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Both my parents migrated here in 2002. My sister and I were born here. We visit our grandparents in Lithuania.', 'Family; Lithuaniua', '', NULL, NULL, 'Petra', NULL, 0, 0),
(2247, '2242', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'Native American and aboriginal culture.', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2248, '2243', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Italy;USA', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'After living all my life in Italy, I went to New York city for 3+ years. My visa expired and then I came here. It has been 2+ years in the UK and 2 days in London.', 'Family;New York;Italy;UK;assimilation', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2249, '2244', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Forced Migration/Enslavement', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'No details', 'Guyana', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandpa lived in Guyana and India, his family moved to Kenya like many other Indians (part of a movement for a better life). Soon after, due to growing racism, they were forced to leave (close their businesses, etc.), they had 3 months. My grandpa moved by himself (age 11) to London (the only place willing to accept Asians at that time).', 'family;Gujana;racism;assimilation', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2250, '2245', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'Among the found photographs there is someone who seriously resembles my mother who emigrated from South Ireland.', 'Family;Ireland;third person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2251, '2246', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Morocco;Gibraltar', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents were born in Gibraltar and Fez. They migrated here in 1948 and I was born in 1952 in SE, London and largely brought up in Peckham. ', 'Family;Gibraltar;Fez;assimilation', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2252, '2247', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Italy;Ghana', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Both my mom and dad came to London (from Italy and Ghana) for better work and life. I have been here for 23 years and still feel like an outsider by the government.', 'Family;Italy;Ghana;politics;alienation', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2253, '2248', 'Angeiza', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Dominican Republic', 'Disc', 'My Migration Story', NULL, 'My name is Angeiza. I came from the Dominican Republic to have a better future.', 'Family;Dominican Republic', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2254, '2249', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ecuador', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mother lived in Ecuador for 20 years of her life until she moved to London, England. ', 'Family;Ecuador', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2255, '2250', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'I would love to see stories of what happens to places after we migrate away from them and what they mean? Potentially would love to learn how to combat anti-immigration.', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2256, '2251', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'St. Lucia;Jamaica', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My daddy is from the amazing country, St Lucia. He came to the UK in 2008 (23 years old). Both of my mummy’s parents are Jamaican. This means I am first and second generation.', 'Family;St lucia;Jamaica', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2257, '2252', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Australia', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'Both my parents were “10 Poros” leaving the UK in 1952 for Australia. They came out with their families and then met in Sydney. They settled and later on passed away 10 and 5 years ago. They left London to have what they considered a better life.', 'Family;Australia;UK', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2258, '2253', '', NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents came here in the late 1950\'s. My father came first, then my mother, and 5 siblings to England, London. I was born here in England, youngest of 9 children. Although they say slavery has passed, it has never been forgotten because I too feel victimised in this country. I too feel like I am living under the borders of slavery.', 'Family;politics', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2259, '2254', '', NULL, '1960s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Poland', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I moved to the UK in 1966, to work for a year. (My parents are of Polish/Jewish heritage). I met a Greek Cypriot in 1968, and we have lived here ever since. This is really our home!', 'Family;work;assimilation;friends', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2260, '2255', NULL, NULL, '1650s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Both parents (Irish) arrived in the 1950s. They were in London  when the signs in the windows of houses said “NO BLACKS, NO DOGS, NO IRISH”. They left in 1972 because of the economic downturn (and anti-Irish sentiment) because of troubles. 2 of their 3 children (born in the UK) now live in England again. The ‘acceptable face of racism’ in England has always seen prejudice against the Irish. As I speak with an English accent, it is fun to correct and caution such behaviour when it happens. Stand up! Speak out!\n', 'Family;racism;politics', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2261, '2256', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Forced Migration/Enslavement', NULL, NULL, 'Cyprus', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'My parents escaped the Cyprus conflict for a better future and their safety. Thank you England!', 'Family;Cyprus;war', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2262, '2257', 'Marco', 'm.munozuk@gmail.com', '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Ecuador', 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'My name is Marco, a refugee from Ecuador. I would like to see more from Latino American emigration. It is a very important issue in the Latino world. This is an amazing place.', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2263, '2258', '', NULL, '1980s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Morocco', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My mother’s family emigrated to the UK from Morocco in the early 1980\'s. They settled in Preston. My mom now lives in Lewisham with my family. ', 'Family;Morocco', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2264, '2259', '', NULL, '2020s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to England in January 1988 as a visitor. Today (December 2021), I am still visiting. Too many places to visit. Let me move on. Thanks!', 'Culture', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2265, '2260', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Wales;Scotland;South Korea;Taiwan;London', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Born in Wales (22 years), Scotland (4 years), South Korea (2 years), Taiwan (5 years), London (3 months). No one prepares you for the constant goodbye’s. The feeling that I will never see someone again, that I will always miss someone no matter where I am. My life is now a spider web of connections.', 'Family;wales;Scotland;South Korea;Taiwan;London;weelbeing', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 1, 1),
(2266, '2261', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'India;Italy', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'One of my grandmothers migrated to England from India when she was 10. My other grandmother moved from Italy in her twenties.', 'Family;India;Italy', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2267, '2262', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Africa', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My father has emigrated from Africa.', 'Family;Africa;third person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2268, '2263', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', 'No details', 'No details', 'Germany', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I grew up in East Germany. After the war calmed down, I traveled to London. On my first stay I met my true love and we are still together. I migrated for love!', 'Family;Germany;friends', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2269, '2264', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'But I feel for those who suffer a lot during their journey of migrating, wanting a better future for themselves. May God bless you!', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2270, '2265', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Mongolia', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mom migrated here from Ulanbaatar, Mongolia and my grandparents migrated to England from Ireland.', 'Family;Mongolia;ireland', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2271, '2266', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'Regular rotating/changing stories in the front space of the museums. Would be nice in particular for locals who visit the museum regularly. ', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2272, '2267', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'No details', 'No details', 'Thailand', 'Disc', 'My Migration Story', NULL, 'I grew up in Bangkok and Penang, although my family is from Singapore. I moved to Bristol for university and now London for my postgrad. Sometimes it feels strange and unfortunate not having a home, but I have found joy and wonder in finding places of home everywhere. ', 'Family;education;assimilation;alienation', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2273, '2268', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'About people migrating from Poland.', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2274, '2269', '', NULL, '1940s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Forced Migration/Enslavement', 'Love', 'No details', 'Iraq', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'In 1948, my mother (Iraqi-Jewish) left Iraq to move/live in a tent in israel. Her family (10 brothers and sisters) all lived in one room in a tent for 5 years. My mother met my Dad when on holiday in the UK - they fell in love, married and had 3 children (me being the youngest!). I feel very privileged to be a British citizen. ', 'Family;iraq;assimilation', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2275, '2270', '', NULL, '1860s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'USA', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'Many generations ago, relatives on my Dad’s side of the family migrated to the US (=1680\'s). I grew up in the US, but migrated to the UK 12 years ago.', 'Family;USA', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2276, '2271', '', NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'India', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandparents migrated to the UK from India in the 1950\'s. They settled in the Midlands, which is where my parents met. I now live in SE London with my partner, who is half Australian.', 'Family;India;friends;assimilation', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2277, '2272', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Zimbabwe', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents migrated from Zimbabwe to the UK with my big sister, and we have been here for 21 years now.', 'Family;assimilation;Zimbabwe', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2278, '2273', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Russia;Poland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandparents were Jews from Russia and Poland, escaping persecution. Grandfather made the first Kosher Fishmonger in East End, London. At 17, he arranged a marriage for me, but I ran away. Now I ask, where are any of my relatives? All dead?', 'Family;friends;alienation', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2279, '2274', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Poland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Both of my parents migrated from Poland to find me a better future.', 'Family;Poland', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2280, '2275', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here with my family for a better life. I love the UK. Thank you for taking care of my family!', 'family', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2281, '2276', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Canada', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My father emigrated to Canada from Glasgow in 1948 for his family to follow. But he died in Toronto. Many years later we arranged a headstone for him.', 'Family;canada', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
(2282, '2277', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'No details', 'No details', 'Spain', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Both my parents were invited to the UK from Galicia in Spain to work. With no other choice, they emigrated to Oxford, never with the intention to stay. Four children later, they ended up staying. My mum still has a Spanish passport and can\'t vote in elections. She has spent more of her adult life in the UK, but she will never be British. ', 'Family;Spain;UK;Work;Europe;Third person ', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2283, '2278', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated to London at the age of 11 (2018) for a better education opportunity. I really miss my friends and places I got attached to while living in my native country. However, it is sometimes worth taking the risk :)', 'Family;education;alienation;wellbeing;education', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2284, '2279', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to Lewisham to study and it has been very strange. Growing up not in London, you hear so much about what it is like to be a Londoner and I feel that a lot of it is rooted in racism and anti-migration sentiment.', 'racism;education', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2285, '2280', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Australia', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My dad and his grandparents came from Adelaide, South Australia. (They were children of German and French emigrants).', 'Family;Australia;Germany;France', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2286, '2281', '', NULL, '1970s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Sweden', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here when I was 2 from Sweden. We always intended to go back but for some reason we stayed. I speak Swedish but my accent is from the 1970\'s which is when we left. ', 'Family;Sweden;assimilation', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2287, '2282', '', NULL, '1980s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mom moved to London in 1986. At this point in her life, her parents had died, her brothers were dead, and she was married to her second husband, my dad. The UK was a fresh start for her and for the prosperity of her children.', 'Family;friends', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2288, '2283', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here from Italy in 2005. I found happiness here!', 'wellbeing', '', NULL, NULL, 'Zuza', NULL, 0, 0),
