(2309, '2304', '', NULL, '1980s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'No details', 'No details', 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I left Ireland in the mid 1980\'s when it was in the midst of a terrible recession. We became known as the Ryanair generation. Many of us were graduates. Many of my fellow citizens returned to Ireland but I relocated [?] in London.', 'Europe;Family;Ireland', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
