(2316, '2311', '', NULL, '1940s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Forced Migration/Enslavement', 'No details', 'Economic', 'France', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My father was in the French Navy when WW2 broke out. He joined the Free French and came to England in 1941 and fought with the No 4 Commandos & the Inter Allied Commandos. He always kept his French nationality but lived in the UK from 1946.', 'France;War;England;Ethnicity;UK;Work;Family;Third Person', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
