(2344, '2339', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'Love', 'No details', 'Netherlands;Scotland', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated 26 years ago from the Netherlands, to follow my husband, who was offered work in Scotland. I emigrated with my 2 little girls (1+2). Now, I’m integrated in the UK, but it will never be my home, nor is the Netherlands still my home. I feel between cultures.', 'Netherlands;Scotland;Family;Pride;Culture;Work', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
