(2348, '2343', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'Lesuire/Retirement', NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here to learn English and to start a new life. I now have a lovely partner and a beautiful baby boy. I have been here for five years. My partner also migrated here to study and settled. That’s our story.', 'Language;Family;Education;Assimilation', '', NULL, NULL, 'Saliha', NULL, 0, 0),
