(2355, '2350', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated to ‘Cod Britannia’ – I’ve seen it become more uncool year after year. Or maybe it was just a P.R. stunt…', 'Pride', '', NULL, NULL, 'Saliha', NULL, 0, 0),
