(2361, '2356', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dominica', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Both my parents migrated here from Dominica. It was not an easy time for them but they made London their home. I call myself Black British as I was born in Britain.', 'Assimilation;Dominica;Ethnicity;Family;Race;Third Person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
