(2389, '2384', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'My mother was born in Lancashire and my father in Dundee. They both moved to London 35-40 years ago where they met and I was raised. I have lived in Brindley my whole life. We visit Scotland a lot and it feels very different to be here.', 'Family;Scotland;Culture', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
