(2428, '2423', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Northern Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents left Northern Ireland. This was because as a Protestant and Catholic they were ostracised by family and worried about raising a Catholic with a Prod surname.', 'Alienation;Family;Northern Ireland;Religion', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
