(2492, '2487', '', NULL, '1970s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'No details', 'No details', 'Uganda', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'The ‘Ladma’s’ arrived in Newcastle after being expelled from Uganda by Idi Amin. My grandparents moved to Leicester and I am what I am because of what they taught me and my family. Thank you Nanabapa and Nanima.', 'Uganda;Family;Pride;Education;War', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
