(2522, '2517', '', NULL, '1940s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'Love', 'No details', 'Poland;Scotland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'At the break of World War II my father was taken from his home from Poland to Lisbon. He then joined to Polish forces in Scotland. He never returned home. He married a Scottish woman in London where they lived the rest of their lives and calls London home with a mixed heritage. ', 'Poland;War;Family;Scotland;Friends;Assimilation', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 1, 0),
