(2659, '2654', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'At least one quote from Theresa May a less hostile environment. You’ve let Amber Rudd carry the can just as she has.', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2660, '2655', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Forced Migration/Enslavement', 'Economic', 'No details', 'Italy', 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'My Italian grandfather from Calabria was a prisoner of war and sent to work on a farm on the out skirts of Hull. When the war was over he went back to Italy and met my nana and had an arranged marriage. A few months later he was asked to move back to Hull and work back on the farm. In which he did bringing my nana with him. My nana could not speak a word of English but was taught by her 5 year old neighbour in Hull. They later on had 3 children (on back) and then on to having 4 grandchildren. My grandad died at 76 years old and today my nana is still alive aged 92 and still living in Hull. I would not be here if it wasn’t for my grandparents Elena Renzo and Saverio Renzo.', 'Family;Italy;Language;Third Person;War;Work', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2661, '2656', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', 'No details', 'No details', 'Kenya', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My Dad and Mum came from Kenya. They left when they were 4 years old and 2 years. When they came to England my dad moved to Slough and my mum went to Sheffield.', 'Family;Kenya;Third Person', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2662, '2657', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', 'No details', 'No details', 'Austria', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mother came from Austria and migrated here after marrying my English father after WW2.', 'Austria;Family;Third Person;War', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(2663, '2658', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'I loved the bit of the museum about rock music and its influence on the discussions regarding migration, but I’m interested in seeing the influence of other genres like rap/hip-hop/grime as well.', 'Music', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
