(2759, '2752', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'No details', 'No details', 'Rhodesia;Zimbabwe', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My father was born to Scottish parents in the former Rhodesia. He refused to fight the colonists and fled to the UK, aged 22 with £50, his wife, and baby. A brave man!', 'Empire;Ethnicity;Family;Politics;Rhodesia;Scotland;Third Person;War;Zimbabwe', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 1, 0),
