(2768, '2761', '', NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'Love', 'No details', 'Cyprus', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents came from Cyprus in 1958. Found each other, fell in love and married. They worked hard, claimed NO benefits and respected the laws of the land. My sister and I were born in London. This is our home but we also have our Cypriot culture. Love. Peace. All are equal x', 'Assimilation;Culture;Cyprus;Ethnicity;Family;Pride;Third Person;Work', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
