(3315, '3308', 'Danny Hughes', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Mum and Dad migrated from Ireland. Mum was in the ATS during the war. Dad and Grandad working in London during the war repairing bomb damage.', 'Family;Ireland;Third Person;War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3316, '3309', NULL, NULL, '1940s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'This is the centenary year of my father who was born in 1915, and migrated to London, via Scotland, from Ireland in 1940. Migrants can, and have had a positive role to play in the development of Britain. This should never be forgotten.', 'Family;Ireland;Scotland;Third Person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3317, '3310', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Jamaica', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My father moved here from St Thomas, Jamaica when he was 13 years old. As a ‘coolie’ he often had to prove himself to be accepted in either white, black or Indian cultures. He’s cool and happy now though…!!', 'Assimilation;Culture;Ethnicity;Family;Jamaica;Race;Racism;Third Person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3318, '3311', 'Jasmine', NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Argentina', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'I am born in London, my mum migrated to London in 2000 from Argentina. One of her and mum’s friends were taken away because she was complaining about a thing and now we don’t know where she lives and if she is alive.', 'Alienation;Argentina;Family;Friends;Third Person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 1, 1),
(3319, '3312', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'India', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mum comes from India.', 'Family;India', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3320, '3313', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Trinidad and Tobago', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My dad migrated to the UK from Trinidad and Tobago, with his oldest brother and father. Unfortunately leaving his little brother alone in Trinidad.', 'Family;Third Person;Trinidad and Tobago', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3321, '3314', NULL, NULL, '1960s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'Lesuire/Retirement', NULL, 'India', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Both my parents migrated to London from India, my dad in 1964, and my mum and brothers a year later. My dad was a college vice-principal in India, and came to the UK on a programme recruiting teachers, but worked in a factory and as a postman until he got a job as a teacher in a school for special educational needs. I was born in the UK a few years later. My dad arrived with 3 pounds, built a life here. He moved back to India for a few years after retiring, but found he was too British to be happy there, and we, his family of children and grandchildren, were in London, which will always feel like home. The UK is home and amazing for its diversity – and all that enriches it from many parts of the world.', 'Assimilation;Culture;Family;India;Third Person;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3323, '3316', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My dad migrated here from Ireland to escape the Catholic Church when he was a child. He loved Richmond in west London.', 'Community;Family;Ireland;Religion;Third Person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3324, '3317', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', 'Economic', NULL, 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My nan migrated here from Ireland when she was 14 with her sister who was 16 because there was no work for them in Ireland.', 'Family;Ireland;Third Person;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3325, '3318', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Pakistan', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mummy and daddy came from Pakistan to Lancashire. They worked hard, adapted to the culture and values as well as valuing their own. Brought the best out of us within two cultures. They have done fantastic. Peace out XXX', 'Assimilation;Culture;Family;Pakistan;Third Person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 1, 0),
(3326, '3319', 'Sheila Devi Virasami', NULL, '1960s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Mauritius', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'From Mauritius. Both my parents, Kistnasam Virasami in 1960, my mum Salachee Virasami joined him in 1961. They had four children, and I was born here in 1962. My parents have since passed They enabled to family to grow into 13 grandchildren and 2 great grandchildren. 2 grandchildren grew up and live in Barbados, the great grandchildren are there too. I have a brother and sister in law from Mauritius. I have a sister in law who is half Jamaican. What a beautiful mix of ingredients. Than you, Sheila Devi Virasami – in loving memory to my mother, with much gratitude.', 'Barbados;Family;Mauritius;Third Person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3327, '3320', NULL, NULL, '1980s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Bolivia;Germany', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mum came to England in the early 90s from Germany. My dad came from Bolivia in 1984.', 'Bolivia;Family;Germany', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3328, '3321', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parent came here since my country was being invaded by the Pakistanis. It is very (losteral?) since I would never have dreamt to move to London but it is now home for them.', 'Assimilation;Family;Pakistan;Third PersonWar', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
