(3356, '3349', 'W.B', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Japan', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents migrated here from Japan when young. I was born here and I’m in love with a white indigenous British girl. I’m glad I found her.', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Maria ', NULL, 0, 0),
