(3366, '3359', NULL, NULL, '1970s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Sri Lanka ', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, '40 years ago, my dad came here from Sri Lanka with £5 to his name. His dream was to go to university and in 1991 he did that. 14 years later i did too. All because he made that journey in 1975. ', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Maria ', NULL, 1, 0),
