(3456, '3448', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Irak', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'To Mr Tony Blair – thanks to you I am here since you started the war in Irak, you went in and killed my parents, then I had to flee and seek asylum in Britain. You are a joke!', 'Britain;Genocide;Irak;Politics;War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
