(3460, '3452', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, 'Education', 'Love', 'Germany', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came from Germany after Uni aged 25.  I wanted to stay 1 year, have fun and get some abroad experience, then go back.  Then I fell in love with a Brit, 10 years later, I’m still here, with a child.\n', 'Brit;Culture;Education;Germany', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 1, 0),
(3461, '3453', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'England;France', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born in France and I am Portuguese. But unfortunately I had to migrate to England.', 'England;Ethnicity;France;Portuguese', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
(3462, '3454', NULL, NULL, '1920s', 'Image', 'Emigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Canada', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My parents emigrated to Canada – my father in 1926, my mother in 1930. I obtained my PhD in Chemistry in 1961 and became a professor of chemistry in 1979 and have spent 3 sabbatical leaves in Cambridge, Oxford and Birmingham. Our younger daughter was born in Cambridge. My wife and I are now retired and we moved to her homeland in 2010, we live in E. Dorset. Our older daughter lives in London.', 'Canada;Education;London', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 1, 2),
(3463, '3455', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Germany;New Zealand', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I am from Germany and came here to work. From New Zealand, not here.', 'Germany;New Zealand;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
(3464, '3456', NULL, NULL, '1970s', 'Image', 'Emigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Ethiopia', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came from Ethiopia to study in a university in 1976, couldn’t go back home because of the revolution in Ethiopia. I love this country, but I had to go through all the discrimination and racism. I survived. Never claimed benefit. Things have changed that much. No matter how long you stayer here, you are a second class citizen … C’est la vie!!', 'Education;Ethiopia;Language;Racism', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 1, 1),
(3465, '3457', 'Saminee', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Pakistan', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came from Pakistan. I stay here. I like Britain. My name is Saminee. 26/6/2015', 'Britain;Pakistan', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
(3466, '3458', NULL, NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Canada;England', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I finished my teacher training in April 2012 and three months later I moved tyo England. My family is still in Ottawa, CN (Canada)', 'Canada;Education;England;Ottawa', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
(3467, '3459', 'Erica C', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'England', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born in Madeira and I came to England when I was three years old. I was a long journey. 3 hours to come to England. By-Erica-C', 'England;Madeira', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
(3468, '3460', 'Shahnaz Alatesy', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Bangladesh;Britain', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I come from Bangladesh. I like Britain. My name is Shahnaz Alatesy 26-6-2015', 'Bangladesh;Britain', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
(3469, '3461', 'Nilanjana', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'Economic', 'Love', 'India;UK', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'To study, work, love and create a new world family. India is my first home and UK my second.', 'Education;India;UK;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
(3470, '3462', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Australia;England;Germany;Ireland', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My grandparents migrated in the 19th century to Australia from Ireland, England and what is now Germany. I’ve lived here in London from 37 years (more than half my life) as an immigrant from Australia, married a man from the Caribbean and have a beautiful daughter who is British, a Londoner with a fantastic heritage. All around the world and back again.', 'Australia;British;Caribbean;Culture;England;Ethnicity;Germany;Ireland', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 1, 3),
(3471, '3463', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Mauritius;UK', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was 5 when I came to thew UK from Mauritius. I spoke very little English. By the time I left primary school, I was in the top of my class!', 'Eduucation;Language;Mauritius;UK', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 1, 0),
(3472, '3464', 'Marielle', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, 'Love', NULL, 'France;UK', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I have migrated here from France 5 years ago. This adventure is amazing and even brough love to my life. I have no plan to come back to France. Thanks, UK for having me! Peace, love and equality for all.', 'France;UK', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
(3473, '3465', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Belgium;England', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born in Belgium. I lived there 9 years with my family. I came to England 3 years ago.', 'Belgium;England', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
(3474, '3466', 'Claire', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'France', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Hello, my name is Claire. I migrated to London and have been living here 3 years. Now I am back to France. Love London', 'France;London', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
(3475, '3467', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I’m lucky, I came here for love, and I learn what I didn’t know about me, about the happiness, the solitude or the friendship. Now I’m different and I like it. Just grateful! Toast', 'Friends', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
(3477, '3469', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Love and Peace, White and Black, no difference. I migrated here for a better and safer life. I have been experiencing different cultures and I never thought of being a racist, because at the end of the day we are all the same!', 'Black;Culture;White', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
(3478, '3470', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated because I’m au pair for four months. I with Bruna a friend, he migrated here because he was alone in his life and his brother didn’t love him.', 'Family;Friends', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
(3479, '3471', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I am from Buenos Aires and I came here to study acting. I am about to finish my degree and I plan to stay here.', 'Buenos Aires;Education', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
(3480, '3472', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Canada', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Search for a change of scenery, I moved here from Calgary, AB, Canada. With roots from Hong Kong, I enjoy the blackcurrant flavours of the UK; it tastes like Dad’s favourite treats. Now, I teach English to English children.', 'Calgary;Canada;Culture;Education;English;Food;Hong Kong;Language', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 1, 0),
(3481, '3473', 'Alex', NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My wife migrated here in 2011. Now we have a little man.', 'Family', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3482, '3474', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Sri Lanka', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I arrived in London when I was 8, with my mum and sisters. We left all our family in Sri Lanka. I remember being very excited because I was coming to the place where the Famous Five (children’s book characters) lived. I love London and I live here with my own children now.', 'Assimilation;Culture;Family;Sri Lanka', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3483, '3475', 'Kasie', NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Hi, my name is Kasie, I came to UK 4 years ago. I found here job opportunities. I have beautiful baby. I’m so happy.', 'Assimilation;Family;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3484, '3476', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', NULL, NULL, 'Australia', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born in Grafton, Australia. I migrated here in 2005 with my British husband. It’s fascinating to think I am returned to the shores my great-great-something grandparents were exiled from when they sailed as convicts in the First Fleet.', 'Australia;Empire;Family', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 1, 0),
(3485, '3477', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I don’t remember why I came. It’s very cold…', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3486, '3478', NULL, NULL, '1990s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Netherlands', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated from the Netherlands in 1999 to follow my dreams and join the creative heart of Europe. 16 years later my kids are British and feel like a proper Londoner.', 'Assimilation;Culture;Family;Netherlands', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3487, '3479', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', 'Economic', NULL, 'Australia', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came from Sydney via Beijing. My girlfriend is Scottish so we decided to move to the UK and further our careers here. I’m a music composer so it\'s pretty thrilling to be in a country that has such a rich history in the arts.', 'Australia;China;Culture;Friends;Music;Scotland;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3488, '3480', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Sweden', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I am half Finnish and Russian and I lived in Sweden for 10 years, after moving around in Europe.  I moved to London to study architecture 6 years later I’m still here.  Thank you!', 'Assimilation;Education;EU;Finland;Russia;Sweden', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3489, '3481', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'Love', NULL, 'Japan', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to England from Japan to study at a university. I met someone there and came back to live with him. I love living in London.', 'Assimilation;Education;Friends;Japan', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3490, '3482', NULL, NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Italy', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came from Italy here in UK 2 years ago hoping in a better future and job. Now I have to go back but it will be always in my heart this great experience that let me grow up a lot.', 'Italy;Pride;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3491, '3483', NULL, NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Turkey', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to Britain 1 year ago from Istanbul, Turkey, studying in London, doing a masters, and becoming part of broader London life and culture has always been a dream to me. Achieving my dream, good days had approached.', 'Culture;Education;Pride;Turkey', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3492, '3484', 'Shoni Newell', NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Jamaica', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to Britain in July 2001. I graduated from high school in Jamaica, I was 16 years old and have lived in Britain ever since. I am now a lawyer and return to the Caribbean to visit family and for rest and relaxation.', 'Education;Family;Jamaica;Wellbeing;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', 'Shoni Newell (30)', 0, 0),
(3493, '3485', NULL, NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Sweden', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I moved here from Sweden in 2012 to study at Kingston University. I’m graduating this year and have no intension to go back … at least not yet.', 'Assimilation;Education;Sweden', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3494, '3486', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My parents did not want me to live like they did - without a future or education, so when I was small my parents left their life and family with me so I was able to achieve what I dreamed and live a better life.', 'Education;Family;Pride', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3495, '3487', 'Andra', NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born on 24 December 2004. My parents name is Anne…… and …… My street names are Korder and Ake. I am half African and British. My teacher is from Canada. (Not very legible)', 'Africa;Canada;Family;Race', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3496, '3488', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Sri Lanka', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I’m Sri Lankan. My parents are my roots to a world far away. I was born here but I migrated here too.', 'Family;Sri Lanka;Wellbeing', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3497, '3489', 'Christina', NULL, '2010s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Romania', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Came here in 2011 from Romania. We’ve always wanted to ‘Go West’; now my family is scattered around the world. I don’t feel rooted to one place. I feel European.', 'EU;Family;Romania', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3498, '3490', 'Ginger', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I ’migrated’ here (in London) for six months and it was a lovely experience. I think migration is normal in this ‘world’, it is not a crime as most people believe.', 'Culture;Pride', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3499, '3491', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Maps of France with arrow to UK drawn on disc.', 'France', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3500, '3492', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, 'Germany', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born in Germany and came to London to Study. I now feel like European citizen. I belong anywhere. I think the word migrant is no longer needed.', 'Culture;Education;EU;Germany', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3501, '3493', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'South Africa', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'South Africa/ After setain issues back home I came here with my sister and my mum.', 'Family;South Africa', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3502, '3494', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Kenya', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here (the UK, first Northampton, then London) with my parents & siblings from Kenya almost 20 years ago. Whilst I miss certain things about Kenya, the UK has many positives and I love the diversity and vibrancy of London in particular.', 'Assimilation;Family;Kenya;Wellbeing', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3503, '3495', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated to London some time ago from the Celtic Fringe of S.W. It’s a funny place!', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3504, '3496', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Guyana', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born in Guyana and moved over here (UK) as a baby. Neither of my parents are British and I suppose neither am I, but because I have been brought up here, I feel British in my heart.', 'Alienation;Assimilation;Family;Guyana', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3505, '3497', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Nigeria', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I was born on the coast of West Africa and was raised in Nigeria. My father died so I came to the UK.', 'Africa;Family;Nigeria', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3506, '3498', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Pakistan', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'Born in Pakistan. Moved before age of 1. Chilling every since.', 'Pakistan', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3507, '3499', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Netherlands', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'A Dutch girl moved from Portugal for here, not sure what I am.', 'Ethnicity;Netherlands;Portugal', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(3508, '3500', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I only meant to come to London for two months and I ended up staying 11 years. I fell in love with the city and never wanted to leave it.', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'PKY', NULL, 0, 0),
(3509, '3501', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'USA', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I cam [sic] from the USA. My grandparents migrated to USA: one pair from Italy and then one from England and one grandparent from Northern Ireland. I am a mongrel – celebrate our diversity, it is our strength!', 'Ethnicity;Third Person;Pride;USA', '', NULL, NULL, 'PKY', NULL, 0, 0),
(3510, '3502', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'New Zealand', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came from New Zealand also known as Roteoaroa, land of the lang white cloud…! I have been here for two years. Good times.', 'New Zealand; Pride', '', NULL, NULL, 'PKY', NULL, 0, 0),
(3511, '3503', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated so it’s good', 'Pride', '', NULL, NULL, 'Sasha', NULL, 0, 0),
(3512, '3504', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Romania', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came from Romania to London with my family.', 'Family;Romania', '', NULL, NULL, 'Sasha', NULL, 0, 0),
(3513, '3505', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Scotland', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I migrated here from Scotland.  I wouldn’t call myself an immigrant, I just moved here with my family.', 'Family;Scotland', '', NULL, NULL, 'Sasha', NULL, 0, 0),
(3514, '3506', NULL, NULL, '1970s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'Child Migration', NULL, 'USA', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My father was part of the brain drain of the 70s. He was a physicist. We moved as a family to the US. After my parents died, I moved back to the UK when I turned 40. ', 'Family;USA;Work', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(3515, '3507', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'India', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I come from India with my family and my life in England is better and I like England.', 'Assimilation;Family;India;Pride', '', NULL, NULL, 'Sasha', NULL, 0, 0),
(3516, '3508', 'Veronica ', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Spain', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My name is Veronica(22) and I’m from Spain. I came here because there is no chance for a new designer to have a future in Spain nowadays. Hopefully, when Spain\'s situation changes I’ll be able to come back to my beautiful country.', 'Work;Spain;Europe', '', NULL, NULL, 'Satakshi ', NULL, 0, 1),
(3517, '3509', NULL, NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration;Emigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Kolkata;India', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'My parents met here in the 50s and I was born in Glasgow. My parents returned home to Kolkata, India in the 60s and I went with them 5 years old. 25 years later, I returned to London , my family followed me except my dad.', 'Family;Kolkata;India;Glasgow', '', NULL, NULL, 'Satakshi ', NULL, 0, 0),
(3518, '3510', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to London because I wanted to learn the language, my original idea was to stay here 2-3 months and I ended up staying here nearly 10 years. Don\'t regret.', 'Language', '', NULL, NULL, 'Satakshi ', NULL, 0, 0),
