(3647, '3639', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'I wish I knew more about it but all I know is that my father’s parents were Jewish immigrants. They covered it up and when asked they wouldn’t elaborate further than ‘yes, we’re Jews’.', 'Family;Religion', '', NULL, NULL, 'Patryk', NULL, 0, 0),
