(3663, '3655', 'Pompom and Jerrie', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Gibraltar;Spain', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My great grandad ‘pompom’ and grandpa Jerrie migrated here from Spain/Gibraltar. Grandad Pompom fought in the war and was positioned in Egypt! RIP both of you.', 'Egypt;Gibraltar;Spain;War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Patryk', NULL, 0, 0),
