(3665, '3657', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Germany;Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My maternal grandmother migrated here from Nazi occupied Germany. She was a German Jew. My grandmother on my father’s side migrated here from County Cork, Ireland. A mix of German Jew + Irish catholic', 'Family;Germany;Ireland;Religion', '', NULL, NULL, 'Patryk', NULL, 0, 0),
