(3941, '3933', NULL, NULL, '1930s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Austria-Hungary; Czech; Poland', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My father’s father, Eugene, was a Czech jew who came to the England London in 1939 with a work permit, as a pastry chef. All but 2 members of his entire family were killed by the Nazis. My mother’s parents were Jews from Poland & Austro- Hungarian, driven out earlier by Pogroms. ', 'Austria-Hungary; Family; Czech; Poland; Third Person; War; Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Tracy Monney', NULL, 0, 0),
(3942, '3934', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Poland; Ukraine', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandpa was from Ukraine and my grandma from Poland. They don’t remember them at all. ', 'Family; Poland; Third Person; Ukraine', '', NULL, NULL, 'Tracy Monney', NULL, 0, 0),
(3943, '3935', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Poland', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'Both of my mother’s parents came to England after being deported from Poland during World War 2. They met in a refugee camp here, got married and started a family. If England hadn’t been so welcoming their lives would have been much worse as orphans in a Communist country (and I wouldn’t be here!) ', 'Assimilation; Family; Poland; Third Person; War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Tracy Monney', NULL, 0, 0),
(3944, '3936', NULL, NULL, '1930s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Poland', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'From Poland in 1930s to flee from Nazis. The only one of her family to come and the only one to avoid concentration camps.', 'Family; Poland; Third Person; War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Tracy Monney', NULL, 0, 0),
(3945, '3937', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Italy; Scotland', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'We believe my grandfather is Italian but is a foundling so no information available. Surname Long is Irish, married a Scot but born and lived in London for 56 + years. Loving it! ', 'Family; Italy', '', NULL, NULL, 'Tracy Monney', NULL, 0, 0),
(3946, '3938', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Australia', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandmother on my mothers side came from Australia during world war 2 to marry some navy guy. They got divorced some time in the 70s… well doesn’t always work out, right? \n', 'Australia; Family; Third Person; War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Tracy Monney', NULL, 0, 0),
(3947, '3939', NULL, NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jamaica', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandmother came to Britain from Jamaica in 1958. My grandfather had arrived one year earlier, She spoke of his perception of Britain with Gold linen and hope. Britain was supposed to be her motherland and always considered herself British. ', 'Family; Jamaica; Third Person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Tracy Monney', NULL, 0, 0),
(3948, '3940', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Poland', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandfather on my father’s side came here in the early 20th century to escape Jewish Pogroms in Poland - My grandmother’s family had also come a generation earlier for the same reason. Our diversity is our strength. ', 'Family; Poland; Third Person; War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Tracy Monney', NULL, 0, 0),
