(3957, '3949', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jamaica', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My father’s parents were both descendants of slaves in Jamaica, one’s parent were brought here as slaves, the other came over on the Windrush after WWII, settling in Neasden, Brent -> 40 years later I came along :) ', 'Assimilation; Empire; Family; Jamaica; Third Person; War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Tracy Monney', NULL, 0, 0),
