(4019, '4012', NULL, NULL, '1910s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Poland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandfather (Aaron Pulman) left Poland in 1910 and came to London. He was an orthodox Jew and left because of laws that banned Jews from the professions.', 'Ethnicity;Family;Poland;Politics;Race;Racism;Religion;Third Person;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
