(4240, '4233', NULL, NULL, '1920s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Russia;Palestine;Poland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'Three of my grandparents migrated here. I never met my dad’s parents/ His father was from Russia and his mother was born in Palestine. My mother’s father was Polish. They were all jewish immigrants and arrived here in the early 20th. That was not a confessional age. When people made a new life they didn’t talk to their children about their experiences. After they passed away, my mother expressed regret that she didn’t hear the full story of their early experiences but it was probably too painful to recall.', 'Family;Russia;Palestine;Poland;Europe;Ethnicity;Race', '', NULL, NULL, 'Satakshi ', NULL, 1, 0),
