(4288, '4281', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, 'Hungary', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandmother is from Hungary. In the war she was hidden by nuns in Budapest to escape the death camps. She came here after the war and became a psychotherapist', 'Europe;Family;Genocide;Healthcare;Hungary;Religion;War;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Maria', NULL, 0, 0),
