(4321, '4314', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration;Immigration', 'Love', 'Economic', NULL, 'Singapore', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandfather emigrated from Singapore and married my grandmother who was half chinese and half white. I’ve heard he wasn’t very nice but he was a shrewd businessman, could count money by flicking through thick wads and was a talented linguist.', 'Celebration;Commerce;Ethnicity;Family;Language;Race;Singapore;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Grace W', NULL, 0, 0),
