(4736, '4729', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Kosovo', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My father came to England from the war-torn country of Kosovo seeking refuge. He was a builder now living + loving life and he’s a bae for doing so, otherwise I wouldn’t have been made.', 'England;Family;Kosovo;Third Person;War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Kirill', NULL, 0, 0),
