(5279, '5271', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Canada;Ireland;Scotland', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'Aside from my grandfather who came from ireland all my family are from scotland. I was born in scotland but moved to london 10 years ago. A lot of my mothers family emigrated to canada after the war.', 'Canada;Family;Ireland;scotland;War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu', NULL, 0, 0),
(5280, '5272', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'Migrants are following the ‘advice’ of Norman Tebbit, by getting on their bikes. How strange that this ‘advice’ is now considered unacceptable by so many people in the UK.', 'UK;politics', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu', NULL, 0, 0),
(5281, '5273', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'I grew up in the north east of england. To my knowledge my family have been there for generations. My grandmother was a domestic servant + grandfather a farm labourer. Changes in education, women\'s rights have meant I was able to go to university + receive a grant. I am the first to get a degree. This led to my being able to live as an independent woman.', 'Education;England;Family;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu', NULL, 0, 0),
(5282, '5274', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Australia', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'My grandparents on my dads side came from bradford, on my mother’s side from Derbyshire and London. I was born and bred in kent but am moving to australia for a year!', 'Australia;Bradford;Derbushire;Family;Kent;London', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu', NULL, 0, 0),
(5283, '5275', 'Fred Sims', NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'Although i have no known immigrants in my recent background, my grandmother’s maiden name was Goodman which seems to have Jewish origins. She was born in Northamptonshire & worked in the shoe trade! Fred Sims born in Dagenham, Essex.', 'Culture;Essex;Jewish;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu', NULL, 0, 0),
(5284, '5276', 'Dwada Jatta', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'Lesuire/Retirement', NULL, 'Gambia', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'My name is Dawda Jatta from the Gambia. I am a student on holidays in UK. I Came to UK to visit relatives and also explore the UK.', 'Education;Family;Gambia', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu', NULL, 0, 0),
(5285, '5277', 'R.N.', NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'I have travelled very many countries and UK is the best as it has all the facilities for disabled people. I like the respect of human life in UK. the education system by R.N. Born in Entebbe by british parents.', 'Etenbbe;UK', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu', '*potentially my migration story instead*', 0, 0),
(5286, '5278', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'I never thought of Herbie as an immigrant but he was and he was our daily friend from Ceylon (as was). He taught us kindness, good manners and a lot of *missing word* that lights up all our lives Thanks God Bless Mike & Jo', 'Ceylon;Friends;Third Person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu', NULL, 0, 0),
(5287, '5279', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'France', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'As far as we can trace back, my family have all come from Dorset/Devon in the UK. I think we first came here in 1066 with William the Conqueror from france. Hopefully our family history will get more exciting in the future. As of 2014 it had its first married lesbians in it <3 :) Me xx', 'Empire;Family;France;LGBT;uk', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu', NULL, 0, 0),
(5288, '5280', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'I was born in Hackenry London, my mummy is from Brighton. My dad is from london. I am 4 years old.', 'Brighton;Family;Hackney;London', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu', NULL, 0, 0),
