(5291, '5283', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Belgium', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'I am a brit who grew up abroad; my parents (from Liverpool & Brighton) work for the EU in Belgium. While I have a UK passport, and English is my mother tongue, I also speak fluent French and other languages. I’ve been in the UK since 2001 but my formative years were spent in Belgium', 'Belgium;Brit;Culture;English;EU;French;Languages;UK', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu', NULL, 0, 0),
