(5293, '5285', NULL, NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Australia', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'My grandmother emigrated to Australia in 1951 - but moved back to Lincolnshire in 1953. I think she missed her twin sister too much.', 'Australia;Family;Lincolnshire', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu', NULL, 0, 0),
