(5376, '5368', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Belgium;England;Netherlands;Scotland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'I am pan - European. And very proud my father migrated here when he was three years old. My grandfather (Belgium) fought for the ali’s & met my grandma whilst serving. She was from Holland & they both fled the war & ran away to Scotland - where my uncle & aunty were born. They reburned to Holland where my father was born - before coming to England to settle. My mum was born here but her father (Danish) migrated here where he met my mum’s mum (Irish) - we are all citizens of world - boarders are just lines on a map', 'Assimilation;Belgium;Culture;Danish;England;Ethnicity;European;Family;Irish;Netherlands;Scotland;Third Person;War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 1, 0),
(5377, '5369', 'Adrian Jones', NULL, '1960s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'St. Lucia', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Both my parents migrated to England London, in the late 1960’s from St. Lucia. They both travelled alone to meet their mother’s who had migrated to England a few years before. - Adrian Jones', 'England;Family;London;St.Lucia;Third Person ', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu Shabu', NULL, 0, 0),
