(5705, '5697', 'Anas Ali', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Bangladesh', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mum is from Bangladesh and my dad is from Bangladesh. My mum went to Manchester and my dad stays in Bangladesh. Then my mum went back to Bangladesh and met my dad. Then they both went to London and they are still living there. Bangladesh flag -> 🇧🇩🏁', 'Bangladesh;Family;London;Manchester;Work', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
