(5731, '5723', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Emigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'No details', 'No details', 'USA', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My grandparents came to London after the end of WW2. They raised my dad and his brother in London. My dad immigrated to the US after he met my mom. They continue to live there today.', 'Family;London;USA;War', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 1, 0),
(5732, '5724', 'Cecilia', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Brazil', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My mum is from Brazil and she came to London', 'Brazil;Family;London', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anandu', NULL, 0, 0),
(5733, '5725', NULL, NULL, '1940s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Poland', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My parents were refugees from Poland after WW2 and I was born in a refugee camp in Wiltshire. Although I’ve lived most of my life in Britain I feel more polish. Polish childhood never leaves you!', 'Alienation;Culture;Family;Poland;Third Person;War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 1, 0),
(5734, '5726', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Nigeria', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My 2 grandparents emigrated from Nigeria. I don’t know why, but I know it was for a good reason', 'Family;Nigeria', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(5735, '5727', NULL, NULL, '1930s', 'Image', 'Emigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Australia', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My maternal grandfather\'s sisters (Great Aunts?) migrated to Australia in the 1930s (?) for a better life. Their family came from Bermondsey. Their father was a drinker who ended his day in the workhouse. Their mother had a breakdown and lived out her days in an Asylum in Surrey. I guess they had nothing to stay for. I visited one of my great Aunts in 1988. She lived in Perth at this time. They had not mentioned contact with out family and were so very Australian by the time of my visit - it was strange experience but nice to meet them', 'Assimilation;Australia;Culture;Family;Healthcare;Third Person;Wellbeing;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', 'Also mentions visit in 1988', 0, 0),
(5736, '5728', NULL, NULL, '1870s', 'Image', 'Emigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'USA', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My great - great grandfather migrated to San Francisco in 1870 escaping the cotton mills of east Lancashire, He died there in 1912 surviving the San Francisco earthquake six years previous', 'Family;Third Person;USA', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 1, 0),
(5737, '5729', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration', 'Love', NULL, NULL, 'Australia;South Africa', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'One of my sisters moved to Australia and another one of my sisters moved to South Africa with her Husband Luke. My whole family really misses them, my sisters Lucy said she might come back for christmas with her Husband luke', 'Australia;Celebration;Family;South Africa;Third Person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(5738, '5730', NULL, NULL, '1960s', 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Argentina', 'Disc', NULL, NULL, 'Argentina - my mum. She met my Geordie Father who installed the 1st computer in the Maths dept of Buenos Aires University in 1961 (?) He was the son of an illiterate miner. My father died in 1969', 'Argentina;Education;Family;Third Person;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 1, 0),
(5739, '5731', NULL, NULL, '1990s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Albania', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'I came to this country aged 2 in the 90s on a boat smuggled along with many others. My mother was only 20. She is my her for bringing me here as a scared - for her life person. We are Albana and I love my homelands', 'Albania;Culture;Family;Third Person', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(5740, '5732', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', 'Economic', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My dad (Ranjit) moved to the UK at the age of 16 to have a better life', 'Family;Third Person', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(5742, '5734', '', NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'South Africa', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My dad was an Asian South African. He left his home and family in J’buneg when he could see politics were going the wrong way. He never went back. He met his brother again after 50 years when he came to London. He came to London in the 50s when it was very different. He met and married my mum here.', 'Asia;Assimilation;Family;Politics;South Africa;Third Person', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 1, 0),
(5743, '5735', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'All my family came from East Anglia as far back as we know - I love reading the other family story wall. We are the only ones who’ve left and moved to London', 'Culture;Family', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(5744, '5736', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Education', 'No details', 'No details', '', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'But I migrated to the UK, unexpectedly. I came here to study and made a home and I stayed. I think my journey has been easier than many others became of European passport.', 'Assimilation;Education;Ethnicity;EU', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0),
(5745, '5737', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration', 'Love', NULL, NULL, 'USA', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'My God Father migrated from England to America because of his family but comes to visits every once and a while and we’re going to see him soon', 'Family;Friends;USA', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(5746, '5738', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'Child Migration', NULL, 'Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandparents migrated to London from Ireland when she was 17 to be a cleaner', 'Family;Ireland;Third Person;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(5747, '5739', '', NULL, '1940s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'No details', 'No details', 'Poland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandfather was a Polish prisoner of war who escaped the Nazis occupation and migrated to England in the 1940s. Here he changes his surname from a Polish to an English one.', 'Assimilation;Family;Poland;Politics;Third Person;War', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 1, 4),
(5748, '5740', NULL, NULL, '1980s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'Economic', NULL, 'Jamaica', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came to London in 1989, Jamaica. Have my 3 children, went to university, qualified nurse. UK has been our home', 'Assimilation;Education;Family;Healthcare;Jamaica;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(5749, '5741', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Jamaica', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'All of my grandparents were in born in Jamaica but migrated to the UK for better opportunities regarding work and life in general. They keep our culture + traditions alive through both stories and memories', 'Culture;Family;Jamaica;Third Person;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 1, 0),
(5750, '5742', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ireland;Austria-Hungary', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents and I were all born in London. My dad’s mum is from Ireland and his dad was Hungarian and Austrian. I am super proud!', 'Austria-Hungary;Family;Ireland;Pride', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
(5751, '5743', NULL, NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandpa moved here 1959 - he worked as a KP on a ship to pay his way here, and paid for my grandma’s ticket in 1960. They set up various restaurants and businesses creating community. My family takeaway is featured in this exhibition!', 'Commerce;Family;Food;Pride;Third Person;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', 'Also mentions 1960 (grandmother\'s immigration)', 1, 0),
