(6015, '6007', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'France', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'But… adopted at birth I later discovered my birth father’s line stretched back as a Hugenot, expelled from France… how far back should we look are we all migrants eventually…', 'Family;France', '', NULL, NULL, 'Anna', 'Migration further back in the family', 0, 0),
