(6065, '6057', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'EDM At the end of the day we are all humans - people shouldn\'t feel better than others or lower than others because of where they come from - the colour of their skin or the language they speak. We have a great potential inside us - regardless of borders -... born to be free, born to be happy!', 'Ethnicity;Language;Wellbeing', '', NULL, NULL, 'El', NULL, 0, 0),
(6066, '6058', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'Grenada ', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mother came over to London when she was 12 years old with 6 other brothers & sisters. My father came to London when I was born 22 years ago. They are from Grenada', 'Family;Grenada', '', NULL, NULL, 'El', NULL, 0, 0),
(6067, '6059', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'England;Ghana', 'Disc', 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'I have always considered myself a south Yorkshire woman but on researching my family history I discovered my ancestors came over the UK. WE ARE ALL MIGRANTS My husband is 100% cormil, my daughter ½ Ghananian ', 'Family;Ghana;Lineage;United Kingdom', '', NULL, NULL, 'El', NULL, 0, 0),
(6107, '6099', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Egypt', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Egypt My parents migrated here in the 70’s they moved to Soho. Met a lot of strange people grew a Afro. Moved to Portobello met [Aswad?] + stayed every since + had me + 3 other', 'Family', '', NULL, NULL, 'Lauren', NULL, 0, 0),
(6108, '6100', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Sri Lanka', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'I am happy to have parents who wanted me to have a good education. My parents came from Sri Lanka to escape the war that was happening there. I was fortunate my father went to University in Jaffna and that my parents worked hard here.', 'Education;Family;War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Lauren', NULL, 0, 0),
(6109, '6101', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Nigeria', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My parents were born in Nigeria. I was born in England but befor when I was a baby They decied to move to England because they had me :)', 'Family', '', NULL, NULL, 'Lauren', NULL, 0, 0),
