(6129, '6121', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'India ', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mum (a Hindu) and dad (a Muslim) moved here in 1959 from the Lucknow and Hyderbad respectively. I went to a Catholic school. I think that sums up why Britain is the best country in the world!', 'Christianity;Family;Hinduism;Islam;Religion', '', NULL, NULL, 'Lauren', NULL, 0, 0),
