(6393, '6385', NULL, NULL, '1960s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Child Migration', NULL, NULL, 'India', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'GUPPI My Grandfather was the first to arrive in UK in 1962. He was the first Sikh employee at Bank of England. Both my parents came from India, my dad at the age of 8 and my mum when she’s was 20. We’ve lived here ever since although I’ll probably move back to India with my partner (who is Indian!)', 'Family;Sikhism', '', NULL, NULL, 'Lauren', NULL, 0, 0),
