(6491, '6483', NULL, NULL, '1950s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jamaica', 'Disc', 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'Both of my parents migrated to the UK in the 1950s, aged 19 & 20. Raised 4 children, working for the NHS and British Celenese. Both from JA and never returned.', 'Family;Healthcare;Jamaica;Third Person;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Angus', NULL, 1, 0),
