(6595, '6587', 'Abby', NULL, NULL, 'Image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Disc', 'What would you like to see in our Migration Museum', NULL, 'I would like to see like countries as places, for example instead of shops we have countries and those countries are where migrants come from.', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', 'Abby 6G, James Wolfe', 0, 0),
