(6798, '6790', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Russia', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandparents on my father’s side migrated to Scotland from Russia. My grandfather established a tailoring business in Edinburgh in which my father worked before studying to become a doctor at Edinburgh University.', 'Asia;Commerce;Education;Europe;Family;Russia;Scotland;Third Person;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Alice Di Tella', NULL, 0, 0),
