(6838, '6830', NULL, NULL, '1930s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Forced Migration/Enslavement', 'Child Migration', NULL, 'Germany', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My mother was born in Berlin in 1923 to a Scottish/Jewish father & a German (non-Jewish) mother. He was a professor at the Humboldt University. She was one of his students & became his 2nd wife. He had been interned in WW1 & didn’t fancy being incarcerated again. He left for Canada then London. My grandmother & her 2 children came here in 1939.', 'Germany;Politics;Racism;War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Hongjie', NULL, 0, 0),
