(6928, '6920', NULL, NULL, '2000s', 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Italy', NULL, 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I came here to London in 2004 for work, from North-East Italy. In 2011 I met my husband, a Londoner, and we now have a daughter. I became a British citizen in 2017 in Lewisham. Thank you Lewisham for welcoming me and many other migrants.', 'Family;Italy', '', NULL, NULL, 'Hongjie', NULL, 0, 0),
