(6936, '6928', 'Anaya C', NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Trindad and Tobago', NULL, 'No known migrants in my family', NULL, 'She was also a nurse and saved lives.\nMy nan migrated from trinidad and tobago and decided to settle in the UK where she had my mum and my uncle. But sadly my nan died in 2017. ', 'Family;Trinidad and Tobago;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Hongjie', NULL, 0, 0),
