(6940, '6932', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Lithuania;Northern Ireland;Russia;Scotland', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, '1) MORRY - arrived from Lithuania/Russia in 1898 age 18 months settled in Hackney\r\n2) LENA - Grandparents arrived in Scotland in 1860’s but were told it was America! Settled in Liverpool\r\n3) ELSIE + DAVID - Met in Belfast - 1st generation from Russia spoke only Yiddish\r\nMoved to Liverpool in 1950’s to escape the ‘Troubles’\r\n4) I’m from Southport in Lancashire - my London husband calls me an immigrant! \n', 'Family;Language;Lithuania;Northern Ireland;Russia;Scotland', '', NULL, NULL, 'Hongjie', NULL, 0, 0),
(6941, '6933', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Pakistan', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandad migrated from Pakistan to the UK. It’s incredible to think how this changed the course of generations in my family', 'Family;Pakistan', '', NULL, NULL, 'Hongjie', NULL, 0, 0),
(6942, '6934', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Sweden;USSR', NULL, 'At least one of my parents migrated here', NULL, 'My dad migrated here from Sweeden[Sweden], and my grandfather migrated from the soviet union.', 'Family;Sweden;USSR', '', NULL, NULL, 'Hongjie', NULL, 0, 0),
(6943, '6935', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Hungary;Poland', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'Both of my grandparents migrated to London and stayed after the War. My granny was from Hungary and worked as a waitress at the Ritz and my Grandad was from Poland and was in the Polish Army. Proud of my grandparents.', 'Family;Hungary;Poland;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Hongjie', NULL, 0, 0),
(6944, '6936', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Emigration;Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Canada;Ireland', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'Both grandparents came from Ireland. They settled in deptford in an Irish catholic community. They raised 6 children - some emigrated to Canada, some stayed here.', 'Canada;Family;Ireland', '', NULL, NULL, 'Hongjie', NULL, 0, 0),
(6945, '6937', NULL, NULL, '1900s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', NULL, NULL, 'Germany', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandfather’s family came here from Germany via Holland as economic migrants around 1900. All the men (my grandad, 4 brothers and his Dad) were glass blowers specialising in making gin-bottles. They came to the East End where he met my Nan.', 'Family;Germany;Work', '', NULL, NULL, 'Hongjie', NULL, 0, 0),
(6946, '6938', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Forced Migration/Enslavement', NULL, NULL, 'China;Hong Kong;Philippines', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'During Philippines’ Dictatorship, my grandparents went to Hong Kong to go to the UK. (This is after Hong Kong was a part of the UK). My parents followed shortly.', 'China(Hong Kong);Family;Philippines;Politics', '', NULL, NULL, 'Hongjie', NULL, 0, 0),
(6947, '6939', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Cuba;Jamaica', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'Looking at my family tree, I discovered that my grandmother travel on a boat from Cuba when she was 18 years old. My grandad came over on a boat from Jamaica, using his brother’s name. Both have passed now, but left behind a big legacy.', 'China(Hong Kong);Family;Philippines;Politics', '', NULL, NULL, 'Hongjie', NULL, 0, 0),
(6948, '6940', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'India', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My great grandfather arrived in the early 20th century as a cook from India. He married an English woman and they had 9 children. He is buried in Buckinghamshire.', 'Family;India', '', NULL, NULL, 'Hongjie', NULL, 0, 0),
(6949, '6941', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ireland;Poland', NULL, 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandad was a Polish fighter pilot + settled after WW2 + married my Irish nan. They lived in London for 50 years.', 'Family;Ireland;Poland;War', '', NULL, NULL, 'Hongjie', NULL, 0, 0),
