(7114, '7106', '', NULL, '1950s;1960s', 'Image', 'No details', 'Education', 'No details', 'No details', 'Nigeria', 'Disc', 'Someone in my family emigrated from here', NULL, 'My late parents migrated from Nigeria to London in the late 50s to study law and nursing. They met here and married and left in 1962 to return home with my first brother who was born then. They brought a piece of Africa here.', 'Africa;Education;Family;Healthcare;Nigeria;Third person', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 1, 1),
