(7302, '7294', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Image', 'Immigration', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'India;Ireland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My dad’s family are nearly all originally Irish but lived in an Irish area of Cardiff for generations, working on the docks. My grandfather on my mum’s side was born in India as part of the British Raj. We know we have some Indian heritage on that side, but aren’t sure how much. I <3 migration. ', 'Family;India;Ireland;Wales', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
