(7311, '7303', 'Sumy Pottay ', NULL, '1970s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Economic', 'Love', NULL, 'India', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandad moved to the UK in the 1970s for work from India. He shortly moved the family too. My mum moved here as part of her arranged marriage to my father. I am British Indian and couldn’t be more grateful for the equality and human rights we have. Britain leads the way! Sumy Pottay (P.E teacher). ', 'Ethnicity;Family;India;Pride;Work', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
