(7313, '7305', NULL, NULL, '1900s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Love', NULL, NULL, 'France', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandmother came from Paris to marry my English grandfather around 1900. Her father ran a travel business and wrote a guide for English tourists to Paris in the late 1800s. Our family has lived in England ever since. ', 'Commerce;Family;France', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
