(7356, '7348', 'John Bowers QC', NULL, '1910s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', 'Child Migration', NULL, 'Poland;Russia', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My grandpa came from St Petersburg in 1912 to escape conscription to the Russian Army. My grandma left a small town in Poland when she was 3. They arrived in Grimsby. They thought they had a ticket for New York or so the story goes. John Bowers QC. ', 'Family;Poland;Russia;War', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0),
