(7358, '7350', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Switzerland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My great grandfather came from Switzerland in the early 19th century – he worked in domestic service to support his family. My grandmother was from a Huguenot family – came in the 1590s. Although it was a long time ago we still remember her immigrant origins with pride!!', 'Family;Pride;Religion;Switzerland;Work', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 1, 0),
