(7360, '7352', '', NULL, '', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'No details', 'No details', 'No details', 'Poland;Scotland', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'He was a Jew from what is now Poland but as a second son, was not allowed to work. He would have been compulsorily pressed into the Army. He arrived in Glasgow by boat from the Baltic City of Danzig. He married a British Jew from Exeter and founded a successful jewellery and antiques business. ', 'Commerce;Family;Poland;Religion;Scotland;War;Work', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 1, 8),
(7361, '7353', 'Rudra,England', NULL, '1970s', 'Image', 'Immigration', 'Refugee/Asylum', NULL, NULL, 'Uganda', 'Disc', 'At least one of my grandparents migrated here', NULL, 'My nanny left Uganda in 1972 and packed as much as she could, otherwise she would have got killed. But luckily she didn’t get killed. I am very happy. Rudra, England. ', 'Family;Genocide;Politics;Racism;Uganda;War', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
