(20057, NULL, 'Burkhard Hauder', 'burkhard.hauder@ntlworld.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dortmund, Germany', 'Disc', 'I migrated here', NULL, 'I moved here from the old West Germany in 1989, five months before the Berlin Wall came down. In 1984, I worked in Leeds as a language assistant. It was the best year of my life. After finishing university, I moved back to England for work, and I am still here today! Incidentally, my father lived in Silesia, which was transferred mainly to Poland after the war. I went over to see his childhood home a few years ago and even started to learn some Polish. It has taught me so much I was not aware of.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'kiosk', '2024-09-28 11:40:09', 0, NULL),
